Bathobaso
Batho bantsho ke batho ba Afrika

Panana
Panana ke mohlare wa dikênywa.
Pêrêkisi
Pêrêkisi ke mohlare wa dikênywa.
Terebe
Terebe ke mohlare wa dikênywa.
Nariki
Nariki ke mohlare wa dikênywa.
Boithomelo bja mokoti
Boithomelo bja mokoti ka kakareto bo na le dikarolo te tharo te kgolo: mokoti, lebato goba letlapa la go ba le mokoti, le seireleto
Mokoti ganti o epiwa ka bodiba bja dimetara te 3  le metara o 1 wa go putlaganya
Mokgatlo wa ta Maphelo wa Lefase o eleta gore di agwe kgolenyana le dintlo go lekanyeta pharologanyo ya phihlelo ya kgauswi le monkgo
Bokgole bja meetse a go epiwa fase lemeetse a go hwetagala bokagodimo bo swanete go ba bjo bogolo ka moo go ka kgonagalago go fokota kotsi ya thilafato
Mokoti wo o lego letlapeng goba lebatong ga wa swanela go ba le bogolo bja go feta disentimetara te 25  go thibela gore bana ba se wele ka gare ga mokoti
Lesedi le swanete go thibelwa gore le se tsene ka mokoting go fokota phihlelelo ya dinthi
Se se ka nyaka tirio ya sekhurumelo go tswalela mokoti lebatong ge e sa diriwe
Ge mokoti o tlete go fihla go dimetara te 0.5  go fihla godimo, o swanete go hlwekiwa ka go ntha mantle goba mokoti o mongwe o swanete go agwa gomme seireleto se tlowe goba boithomelo bo agwe lefelong le lengwe Taolo ya go tloa seretse sa mantle ka mokoting e tloga e hlakahlakane
Go ba le dikotsi ta tikologo le maphelo ge e sa sepetwe botse.
Boithomelo bja mokoti bjo bo tlwaelegilego bo ka kaonafatwa ka mekgwa e menti
Mokgwa o mongwe o akareta go tsenya phaepe ya go tsenya moya ka gare ga mokoti godimo ga moago
Se se kaonafata tshepeto ya moya le phokoto ya monkgo wa thoilete
Gape e ka fokota dinthi ge bogodimo bja phaephe bo tswaletwe ka polastiki 
Go mehuta ye ya dithoilete sekhurumelo ga se hlokege go ka diriwa go pipa mokoti lebatong
Kaonafato enngwe e ka akareta go aga lebato ka mokgwa woo diela di ka tsenago ka mokoting gomme bogodimo bja mokoti bo agwe ka ditena le semente go kaonafata maatlafato.
Go tloga ka 2013 boithomelo bja mekoti bo akanyeditwe go diriwa ke palo ya batho ba dibilione te 1.77
Se ganti se twelela go mafase a twetwago pele gape le metse selegae lemafelo a leokeng
Ka 2011 batho ba dibilione te 2.5 ga se ba kgone go ba le phihlelelo ya thoilete ya maleba gomme dibilione di fedite di diria lebala go bjalo ka boithomelo tikologong yeo ba lego go yona
Borwa bja Asia le Sub-Saharan Afrika go na le phihlelelo ya bofokodi ya dithoilete
Go dinaga te di twetwago pele theko ya thoilete ya mokoti e bonolo e magareng ga 25 le 60 ya USD
Theko ya tlhokomelo ya go ya go ile e magareng ga 1.5 le 4 ya USD go motho yo mongwe le yo mongwe ngwaga ka ngwaga gape ganti se ga se elwe hloko
Go dikarolo te dingwe ta metse magaeng India go dirilwe tlhabano ya "Ge go se na Thoilete, Go ka se be le Monyadiwa" gomme e diriwa go tlhohleleta basadi gore ba gane go nyalwa ke banna bao ba se nago thoilete.
Hepatitis A
Hepatitis A  ke bolweti bja go fetela bjo oro bja sebete bja go bakwa ke baerase ya hepatitis A 
Makga a manti go ba le diupo te nnyane goba ga go na diupo kudu mo baneng ba ba nnyane
Nako ya magareng ga diupo le phetelo, go bao ba hwetago bolweti, ke magareng ga dibeke te pedi le te tshela
Ge go na le diupo ganti di bonagala dibeke te seswai gomme se se ka akareta: pherogo, go hlata, lethologo, letlalo le serolane, letadi, bohloko dimpeng
Palo ya 10–15% ya batho e itemogela poeleto ya diupo mo dikgweding te tshela morago ga phetelo ya mathomo
Go se ome go oro ga sebete ga nke go diragala ka ge sese tlwaelegile go diragala go batofe.
Ganti e phatlala ka go ja dijo goba go nwa meetse a go thilafatwa ka mantle a go ba le phetelo
Hlapikgepetla ya go se butwe botse ganti ke sehlodi
E ka phatlalatwa ka patamelo ya motho yo a fetetwego
Le ge e le gore bana ga ba laete diupo ge ba fetetwe ba sa kgona go feteta ba bangwe
Morago ga phetelo e tee fela motho wa gona o hweta sontio bophelo bja gagwe ka moka
Tlhahlobo e nyaka diteko ta madi ka ge diteko di swana le ta malweti a mangwe
ke enngwe ya te hlano ta go tsebja ta dibaerase ta hepatitis: A, B, C, D, le E.
Kenti ya hepatitis A e thua kudu ka thibelo
Dinaga te dingwe di e eleta gore e diriwe leboeleta go bana le go bao ba lego kotsing e kgolo bao ba sa kago ba hweta kenti peleng
Go bonagala e na le mohola bophelong
Mekgwa ye mengwe ya thibelo e akareta go hlatswa ka matsogo le go apea dijo gabotse
Ga go na kalafi e iteng, ka khuto le dikalafi ta pherogo goba lethologo di eletwa bjalo ka dinyakwa ta motheo
Phetelo ganti e fola go felela ntle le bolweti bja go twelapele bja sebete
Kalafi ya go se ome ga sebete go oro, ge e ka direga, e ka direga ka palollo ya sebete.
Lefaseng ka bophara palo ya dimilione te 1.5 ta makga a diupo a twelela ngwaga o mongwe le o mongwe ka palo ya dimilione te lesome ta diphetelo
Go tloga go tlwaelegile dileteng ta mafase ao a nago le tlhwekio ya go fokola gape ao a se nago meetse a go hlweka
Go mafase ao a tweego pele 90% ya bana e fetetwe ka mengwaga ye 10 gomme ba ka sontega ge ba gote
Ganti e direga ka tsogo go dinaga te twetego pele ga nnyane moo bana ba sa nkago ba bonthego ge e sa le ba ba nnyane gomme kenti e sa phatlalatwa
Ka 2010, hepatitis A e oro e bakile mahu a 102,000
Letati la Lefase la Hepatitis le twelela ngwaga ka ngwaga ka July 28 go tweleta temoo ya hepatitis ya phetelo.
Malaria
Malaria ke bolweti bja go twa go monang bja go fetela batho le diphoofolo te dingwe te di hlotwego ke dipharasaete ta diprotozoan  ya mohuta wa "Plasmotiamo"
Malaria a baka diupo te di akaretago letadi, malaise, go tlhata le go opa ke hlogo
Mabakeng a kgatelelo e oro e ka baka letlalo le serolana, dikotwane, go idibala goba lehu
Diupo te ganti di thoma go bonagala ka morago ga matati a lesome goba lesome hlano morago ga go longwa
Go batho bao ba sa hwetago kalafo e botse bolweti bo ka boya gape ka morago ga dikgwedi te mmalwa
Go batho bao ba sa twelago go fola phetelo, phetelo gape ganti e laeta diupo te nnyane
Karolwana ye ya thonto e timelela ka morago ga dikgwedi ge eba ga go sa na phihlelelo ya malaria.
Ka tlwaelo, bolweti bo fetetwa ka go loma ga monang wa tshadi wo o fetetwego wa "Anopheles".Go longwa go go tweleta dipharasaete ta go twa mareng a monang ka gare ga madi
Dipharasaete te di sepelela sebeteng moo di golago le go tswala gape gona
Mehuta ye mehlano ya "Diplasmotiamo" di ka feteta le go phatlalatwa ke batho
Mahu a manti a bakwa ke "P.falsiparamo" le "P.vivax", "P.ovale", le "P.malariae" ka kakareto di baka mohuta o bonolo wa malaria
Mehuta ya "P.knowlesi" ga e bake malweti ganti bathong
Malaria e hlahlobiwa ka go dira diteko ta maekroskoupu ya madi ka go diria difilimi ta madi, goba ka diantitene-te di theilwego diteko ta mogololelo
Mekgwa yeo e diriago phetogelo ya ketane ya polymerase go lekola dipharasaete DNA di tweleditwe, eupa ga di diriwe ka bophara mafelong ao malaria a go twelela gona ka lebaka la theko le tharagano.
Kotsi ya bolweti e ka fokotwa ka go thibela go longwa ke menang ka go diria nete ya menangle sekoba dikhunkhwane, goba magato a go laola menang bjalo ka go fothela dopolayakhukhu le go phea meetse a emegego a sa elego
Dikalafi te mmalwa di a hwetagala go sethibela malaria go basepedi mafelong ao bolweti bo tlwaelegilego gona.Tose ya sewelo ya kalafi ya sulfadoxinepyrimethamine e a eletwa go masea le ka morago ga dikgwedi te tharo ta mathomo ta boimana mafelong ao go nago le palo ya godimo ya malaria
Malebana le tlhokego, ga go kgonthago ya kenti  ye e lego gona, le gee le gore maiteko a go e tweleta a dirilwe
Kalafi yeo e eletwago ya kalafo ya malaria ke tswakanyo ya dikalafi ta kgatlhanong le malaria te di akaretago artemisinin
Kalafi ya bobedi e ka ba mefloquine, lumefantrine, goba sulfadoxinepyrimethamine
Quinine mmogo le doxycycline di ka diriwa ge eba artemisinin ga e hwetagale
Go a eletwa gore mafelong ao malaria a tlwaelegilego, go swanete gore malaria a tiietwe pele kalafi e ka thongwe ka lebaka la pelaelo ya palo e kgolo ya kgano ya ditagi ta kalafi
Kgano e twelete go dikalafi te mmalwa ta kgatlhano le malaria mohlala, kgano ya chloroquine- "P.falsiparamo" e phatlalete go mafelo a manti a malaria, gape kgano ya artemisinin ke bothata dikarolong te dingwe ta Borwa-bohlabela bja Asia.
Bolweti bo phatlalete ka bophara dileteng ta molatati le dilete ta magareng ta melatati te di bapanego ka bophara le ekhweitha
Go akaretwa kudu Sub-Saharan Afrika, Asia, le Latin Amerika
Mokgatlo wa ta Maphelo wa Lefase o akanyeta gore ka 2012, go be go na le makga a malaria a palo ya dimilione te 207
Ngwageng woo, bolweti bo lekanyeditwe gore bo bolaile batho ba palo ya magareng ga 473,000 le 789,000, bonti bja bona e be e le bana mo Afrika
Malaria ganti e nyalwanthwa le bohloki gomme a na khueto empe ya twetopele ya ekonomi
Mo Afrika go akanyeditwe go lahlegelwa ke dibilione te 12 ta di-USD ka ngwaga ka lebaka la theko ya godimo ya tlhokomelo ya ta maphelo, go lahlegelwa ke bokgoni bja go oma le tiragato ya boeti.
Geographic coordinate system
Geographic coordinate system
A libaka hokahanya tsamaiso ke hokahanya tsamaiso e thusa hore mong le e mong lefelo Lefateng ho boletse ka ho hlaka ka sete ya dinomoro kapa mangolo
The coordinates ba atisa ho khethiloeng joalo hore e mong oa dinomoro e emela lathe boemo ba, 'me peli kapa tse tharo ea dinomoro emela rapameng
A tloaelehileng kgetho ya koordinaten ke bolokolohi, phahameng.
Ho bolela ka ho toba le lefelo ka tlhakore-pedi Mapa hloka hore 'mapa boqapi.

Bungeni
Bungeni is a sprawling rural settlement situated at the foothills of the Soutpansberg mountain range in the former Gazankulu homeland, Limpopo Province, South Africa
It lies 35km East of Makhado, Bungeni is in the Hlanganani district, on the R578 road between Makhado and Giyani
In 1994, administrative control of this western portion of Gazankulu was allocated to Makhado local municipality, in the Vhembe district
It consists of more than 11 large villages, namely Xikhulu, Mabodhlongwa, Xitaci, Mtsetweni, Xihambanyisi, Nwa-Mhandzi, Xivambu, Nhjakanhjaka A, Nhjakanhjaka B, Wayeni, and Mahatlani
According to the 2015 mid-year population statistics, Bungeni has a population of approximately 30,000 people.
Geologically, Bungeni village is located on the 'tail end' of the Soutpansberg mountain range
When the Soutpansberg range was formed over a billion years ago, it resulted in the formation of broken hills all over the village of Bungeni, which is a Geological feature of Bungeni today
These broken hills at Bungeni village were known as 'Spelenkon Hills' Which stretches from Bandelierkop in the west
The name 'Xipilongo' was derived from the railway station situated near Bandelierkop called 'Grootspelenkon'
The village itself is just less than 6km from Levubu Agricultural plantations and 8km from the Soutpansberg Mountain range
The soil type is the same as those on the Soutpansberg mountain range
Rainfall at Bungeni corresponds to the climate of the Soutpansberg mountain range, with maximum temperatures during summer reaching as high as 34C
The total elevation of the village is 700 metres above sea level.
The name 'Bungeni' is the name of the first son of Nkonwana from his second wife
The hes son was supposed to be Phalani from the first wife of Nkonwana and was the only son from his mother
Bungeni Royal aresvillage was named after him, That is where the name "Bungeni" originated
The village should have been named after the surname of the King 
Naming a village after the surname of the chief is a common practice amongst the Tsonga people, for example, the village of Mbhokota is named after the surname of chief Mbhokota
The village of Bungeni and its Royal Family originates in KwaZulu Natal where they were known as Mazibuko Clan, where they were a powerful ruling class in Pre-Colonial Natal
The Mazibuko Clan dominated and ruled villages on the slope of Drakensberg Mountains in Northern KwaZulu-Natal for centuries
They left KwaZulu Natal in 1700 with their hundreds of followers, headed east and settled on the coastal plains of Mozambique, where they also became senior chiefs or rulers.
There were many reasons why they left or departed KwaZulu-Natal, one of the common reasons was that they have always been attacked by the Zulu clan to the south, who were in their early stages of forming the Zulu Kingdom by invading or killing other clans
At that time, the Zulu were not an ethnic group but were a clan, like the Mazibuko clan, who both spoke an ancient dialect of the Zulu language
The Mazibuko Clan were harassed again and again by the Zulu clan until they finally decided to leave KwaZulu-Natal and to go and found a new kingdom for themselves in Southern Mozambique
Upon arrival in coastal Mozambique, they adopted Xitsonga language and culture and changed their clan name from Mazibuko clan to Mabunda clan or also known in Tsonga as Vahlavi
However, some retain the Mazibuko surnames, while others preferred Mabunda
The Mabunda clan ruled southern Mozambique for more than 110 years and were finally expelled from Mozambique by the invading armies of Soshangane between 1820 and 1825.
Therefore, Bungeni village, as it is known today, is of relatively recent origin
Hosi Bungeni and his subjects arrived here between 1819 and 1820 from Mozambique during the wars of Soshangane, also known as Manukosi and became the Paramount chief of Tsonga refugees in the Spelenkon , Hosi Bungeni exercised Authority over all Tsonga refugees who were fleeing the brutal formation of the Gaza Kingdom by Soshangane in Southern Mozambique, the natural home of the Tsonga people
As Paramount Chief, Hosi Bungeni was responsible for the allocation of land to the Tsonga refugees, the provision of military protection, provision of food, as well as exercising authority over all these refugees.
Upon arrival in Spelenkon as refugees, Chief Bungeni established Bungeni village
Bungeni was a king of sSpilonkeng, but with the introduction of apartheid during the 1960s, Hosi Bungeni was made a Senior Tsonga Chief and ceased being a kingship, by contrast, Hosi Njhakanjhaka was made a Headman who presided over a small village of Shirley, Waterval township, Lemana, Njhakanhjaka village and Mabobo village at a place collectively known as Elim
The authority of Hosi Njhakanhjaka was therefore destroyed over Bungeni Village during Apartheid
Hosi Njhakanhjaka's paramount Chieftaincy was restored in 1995 and is now recognised as a Tsonga paramount Chief.
Chief Bungeni and his people, while in Mozambique, led a rebellious campaign against Nguni invaders, who not only oppressed the Tsonga people but also enslave Tsonga woman and children
Chief Bungeni tried to defend his people but was easily defeated by Soshangane and his soldiers
To avoid death and execution by Soshangane, Chief Bungeni and his followers fled and sought refuge at a place known today as Bungeni, under the protection and authority of chief Njhakanjhaka and was a subject of Hosi Njhakanhjaka
Chief Bungeni was made a senior headman by chief Njhakanjhaka
Another waves of Tsonga migration into Bungeni happen again between 1859-1863 during the civil war between Mzila and Mawewe, the two brother were fighting for a Kingship after the death of their father Soshangane
The last wave of Tsonga migration into Bungeni happened between 1890-1895 during the Portuguese and Nghunghunyane wars.
Hosi Nhjakanhjaka Mukhari, the headman of Spelenkon , along with Joao Albasini, was a chief of all Vatsonga people in a place known today as Hlanganani
A place where Bungeni is situated today was known as Spelenkon  and was one of the most important sites of the Great Spelenkon empire, under the mighty arm of Joao Albasini
Hosi Bungeni was an assistant to Joao Albasini and Hosi Nhjakanhjaka, later, Hosi Bungeni was made a Senior traditional leader by the Apartheid government during the 1960s, a position he did not deserve to hold since he fell under the authority of Hosi Nhjakanhjaka
By contrast, the real paramount chief of the Vatsonga of Spelenkon, Hosi Nhjakanhjaka Mukhari, was made an 'Independent Headman' and was given a Tribal Office at Waterval township, below Elim Hospital
Bungeni village, along with Nwa-Xinyamani, Chavani, Mbhokota, Bokisi, Lemana, Njhakanhjaka , Shirley and Valdezia were collectively known as Spelenkon and became home to thousands of Tsonga refugees fleeing the murderous and oppressive Gaza Kingdom under Soshangane, a Zulu General who has conquered the homeland of Vatsonga people in and around Southern Mozambique.
Soshangane oppressed and terrorised the Tsonga people to such an extent that a wave of immigration into the Transvaal took place, thousands of Vatsonga fled their homes  and settled at Spelenkon
By length, Bungeni share a border with Nwa-Xinyamani and Ha-Mashamba  until Ka-Nkuzana, which is long, its brendth, it share a border with Ha-Mashau  until Bellevue , which is also long, making Bungeni one of the biggest Traditional Authority in the Makhado local municipality
In 2019, Bungeni village will be 200 years old.
Bungeni has 5 secondary schools, which are Russel Bungeni High School, Hluvuka High School, Marholeni Secondary school, Bellevue secondary school and Mahatlani Secondary School
There are 12 Primary schools at Bungeni
There are: Nhjakanhjaka Primary, Muhluri Primary, Mkhono Higher Primary, Bungeni Primary, Xitaci Primary, Mtsetweni Primary, Xihambanyisi primary, Ndlavheya Primary, Nwa-Mhandzi primary, Wayeni primary, Mahatlani primary and Masungi primary.
Health care is extremely poor, there are 2 community clinics, which are Bungeni health centre and wayeni health centre, both are attached to Elim Hospital
HIV and Aids has been a leading cause of death amongst young people but with the availability of ARV's, death toll has slowed down
There is a private medical centre at the Diza complex
A number of traditional healers  still ply their craft in the villages.
There are no specific numbers to add to the claim that HIV and Aids has been the major cause of death among young people
Bungeni remains one of the communities with a domination of elderly people, it might be because of the traditional food such as Tihove, Xiendlahivomu, Ximbhundhwa, Xigugu, Xirhidza, etc
and the lifestyle in general.
Bungeni is one of the most developed villages in the Makhado local municipality
Amongst the most developed section of Bungeni is Nhjakanhjaka A village a small suburban called Mandela and Tana na Pulani has houses and mansion that compete with Makhado Town and other developed areas in the South Africa
The Bungeni 'post office' is situated at Bungeni Xikhulu area.
Nhjakanhjaka A has a fully fledge filling station, Pharmacy, Fresh Loaf Bakery Shoprite U Save complex, Pep Store and Fish  Chips which opened on 27 October 2014 and a community Radio, known as Hlanganani Community radio.The village has seven famous soccer team: Bungeni Young Tigers,Basani Arrow Chiefs,Njhakanjhaka Mighty Chiefs, Nwa-Mhandzi All Dangerous, Bungeni Junior Birds, Mahatlani All Stars  Bungeni New Born.
Bungeni, along with other villages situated in the area, is currently experiencing strong economic growth in the property market
A number of major retail hardware stores operate in the area, selling construction materials
This has led to the once rural villages of the area becoming semi-urban areas.
Well-known people from Bungeni include David Mathebula,Lebo Manyama from Njhakanjhaka , footballers in the South African Professional Soccer League
Jacob Tshisevhe, a former Kaizer Chief defender, was born at Njhakanjhaka Village 
Another notable individual is Falaza Mdaka, who is the Chief Whip of the African National Congress in the Limpopo Legislature
Robert Nkuna who is the former Advisor to the Minister of Transport
Tiyani Rikhotso is a spokesperson in the Department of Transport
Chicco Twala , Judge George Maluleke, North Gauteng High Court 
Dr Risimati Dazmen Mavunda
Son of Jack, son of Vuromo , son of Phalani the sibling of Bungeni
Dazmen was the first black person to qualify in Nuclear Medicine in South Africa
He is now practicing as a chief Physicist at Nuclear Energy Corporation of South Africa 
And is lecturing at University of Johannesburg, Tshwane University of Technology and Venda University.He obtained his primary education at Rivoningo Primary and his parents's home is still at Ribungwani.
Buysdorp
Buysdorp ke village nyane go feta Mmasepala Setereke ta Vhembe wa diporofense Limpopo kamoka Afrika Borwa.
A rural coloured community located 14 km from Vivo, on the R522 road to Louis Trichardt, Buysdorp was named after Coenraad de Buys, the "King of the Bastards" in Sarah Millin's fictional account of his life.

Dzanani ke 40 km ya toropo ya Thohoyandou, 50 km ya Makhado, 420 km ya Pretoria le 690 km ya Harare kô Zimbabwe.

Matsebe Sekhukhune
Sekhukhune goba Matsebe Sekhukhune, , e be e le ngwana wa mathomo go ba bararo ba kgoi Sekwati le Thorometjane
Barwa ba Kgoi Sekwati ke Sekhukhune , Dinkwanyane le Kgoloko
Ka seto sa Bapedi bogoi bo tea ke ngwana wa pele ka morago ga lehu la tatagwe
Matsebe  o rile ka morago ga lehu la tatagwe  ka 1861, a latela seto sa Sepedi ka ge tatagwe e be e le kgoi
O thopile bogoi go morwarragwe Mampuru ka lerumo
Mampuru yeo lehono ba reetego Pretoria Central Prison ka yena, e be e le morwarrago Sekhukhune ka ge mmagwe  a nyetwe ke bakgomana ba gaSekwati
Mampuru o godiitwe ke mmago Sekhukhune  ka lapeng la moate.
Ge Hendrik Potgieter le maole a gagwe  ba hlasela moate wa Bapedi ka piring ka 1838
Sekwati o ba fente empa a tla a lemoga gore moate wa gagwe wa piring ga se wa bolokega ke ge a tlo hudugela Thaba Boego .
Sekhukhune I, e be e le kgoi kgolo ya Bapedi  ba ga Sekhukhune, Limpopo nageng ya Afrika Borwa
O be a dula thabeng ya Leolo, e ago kgona go e ireleta
Naga ya Kgoi kgolo Sekhukhune e thoma ka noka ya Lekwe, south , go fihla ka noka ya Lebepe, north  gape Mogomatse, east  le kgalagadi, west .
Sethaba sa Bapedi se bopa ke mehlobo ya DiTlou le Marota bana baMadi a bogoi!
Batau Manganeng, Masemola, Mogashoa, Bakgaga , Baroka , Bakwena, Bakone , Moletlane le babangwe
Magoi a gaSekhukhune ka Palo 167 le Dintona te 268.
Ba bodikela  ba rile ge ba fihla mo nageng ya gaSekhukhune ba e abaganya ka ge ba be ba nyaka mahumo a naga  ba be ba e reela leina la Transvaal, ge go fihla Maisemane ba e a abaganya gape ba e bita PWV 
Kgoikgolo Sekhukhune o lwete naga ya gagwe goba go fihla Maburu le Maisemane ba kopana ba dira seboka gore ba kgone go ka fenya Sekhukhune.
Sekhukhune o kgonne go fenya ntwa magareng ga Maburu le Maesimane ba le seboka
Goba go fihla Maburu le Maisemane ba eya go hloma seboka se sengwe le Maswatsi ke ge ba kgona go mo swara ba moia ko toronkong ya Pitori .
Leika la kgoro ya Sekhukhune.
Ke leboga tshemisho ya lena e fetolwetjego sepeding
Ke rata go swaela mo erego maisimane a fetotje Transvaal to PWV
PWV ke karolo fela ya borwa bjwa Transvaal, erago Pretoria,Witwatersrand le Vereenaging
Ka kgopela rephosholle gore PWV is another name for Transvaal, Instead the correct one is ZAR- Zuid Afrikaanse Republik which is another name of Transvaal before unification four Republics as Natal Republic, Orange Free State Republic, Cape Colony and ZAR to make up what we today call South Africa-ZA
By so saying Transvaal itself range from VAAL River it the South to LIMPOPO River in the North,Komati in the East and ZeerustRusteburg Western Transvaal
Ke dumela e tla kwagala gabotse.
Gomme kopanyo ya diya Colony tje nne tje ebile ka 1910,in what was to be called Union of South Africa under General Louis Botha as first prime minister.
Kwelagobe Maboko  072 139 1952

Molepolole
Molepolole ke motsemogolo wa Bakwena
Toropo o sekgala sa 52 km bodikela ya toropo kgolo Gaborone.
Molepolole ke boagedi jwa batho ba ka tshwara  dikete tse masome a supa .
Fa motse o o leng gone go ne go bidiwa Dithubaruba fa Bakwena ba tla go aga teng
Ka nako tseo ba ne ba eteletswe pele ke Kgosi Sechele o o neng a ba falotsa mo Maburu  le mo go Mzilikazi wa Batebele.
Kgosi Sebele wa Bakwena ke mongwe wa dikgosi tse tharo tsa Batswana ba ba ileng ba ya ko ga Mmamosadinyana  go ya go kopa tshireletso mo Maburung ba ba neng ba ikgagapelela lefatshe.
Kgosi kgolo ya motse ka nako eno  ke Kgari Sechele
O tsere bogosi jwa gagwe mo go motshwarelela bogosi e bong Rre Kgosikwena Sebele, le fa go ntse jalo Rre Kgosikwema e rile go mo bo rolela ya seka ya nna kgetsi e potlana ka go bo a ne a re bogosi ga bo a lebana Kgari Sechele
Go ya ka tshekatsheko ya ditso tsa bakwena, go le bega ha bogosi bo ne bo lebagane Mokgalagadi Sechele, kgotsa mongwe wa bo monnawe
Le mororo go ntse jalo, Kgosi Kgari Sechele ke ene kgosi ya Bakwena mo bogompienong.
Gaborone
Gaborone , ke leina le le gatisitsweng kana le le biditsweng go reelela toropo ka Kgosi 
Gaborone ke toropo kgolo mo Botswana, e na le palo ya batho ba le 191,776
Dipalo tse di gatisitswe ka ngwaga wa 2006 go ya ka dipatlisiso tsa ba palo batho, se e le sesupo sa gore 10% ya Botswana jotlhe ka bophara e kwa Gaborone.
Toropo ya Gaborone e agetswe fa gare ga thaba ya Kgale le Oodi, fa nokeng ya Notwane, mo borwabotlhaba jwa Botswana, gape e gaufi le molElwane wa Afrika Borwa
Toropo e e, nale lebala la difofane la Sir Seretse Khama kwa difofane di gorogelang teng
Ke kgaolo ya bodiredi le boeteledipele ka bo yone, gape ke motsemogolo wa kgaolo ya metse e e mo borwabotlhaba
Banni ba Botswana ba bita toropo e ba re Gabs kana GC fa ba e boka.
Gaborone o ne a agiwa go nna motsemogolo ka ngwaga wa 1960 fa lefatshe la Bechuanaland Protectorate le tsaya puso, fa e nna lefatshe le le ikemetseng ka nosi
Mo gare ga toropo e go na le madirelo a dikgwebo, marekisetso, le mafelo a ga goromente a agilweng kwa bophirima jwa marekisetso 
Toropo e ke nngwe ya ditoropo tse di golang mo lefatsheng, se se bakile mathata a tlhaelo ya lefatshe le go ipaya mo go seng ka fa molaong
Toropo e e nale dikgotlhang tse di tsenang mo lefatsheng go tswa ko Zimbabwe le Afrika Borwa ka ngwaga wa 1980.
Itsoseng
Itsoseng ke toropo go feta Mmuoselegae wa Ditsobotla wa diprofense Leboa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
The town was established in 1963 on the farm De Hoop as a black township, and became part of Bophuthatswana in 1977
At that time, the town was renamed from De Hoop to Itsoseng.

Coligny ke toropo go feta Mmuoselegae wa Ditsobotla wa profense Leboa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Coligny e 27 km borwa-bohlabela ya Lichtenburg le 88 km leboa-bodikela ya Klerksdorp.

Biesiesvlei e bodikela la Klerksdorp.

Pachsdraai e leboa la toropokgolo Groot Marico le Swartruggens.

Bêa nama
Braai  ke neano tsoang sechabeng e leng lipuo tseo nama pele ko Grill kapa bêa pheha golim ya mashala se chesa ka golo
Neano ea lona qalong o ile a qala le ta Maburu , empa na wa tloha ga namela wa batho ba bang kao fela ba Afrika Borwa, wa akarelletsa le Botswana, Namibia, Lesotho, Zimbabwe le Zambia.
Ntle go moo disementshisi nama, poone, ditapole a foil le li-mushroom ka tloaelo sena galikiloeng, gangata e le lijana lehlakoreng la ka, empa ka linako tse ling e boetse e ka lokisoa joaloka lijong jeng nama.
Joaloka e bolelang boerewors lentsoe, lentsoe "bêa nama" o boetse o akarelletsa Seisimane le lipuo tse ngata ka Borwa ba Afrika.

Simon's Town  ke toropo hleng le Cape Town, Afrika Borwa, ke base ya South African Navy.

The town is named after Simon van der Stel, an early governor of the Cape Colony.

Hlapi le dithipisi
Hlapi le dithipisi ke takeaway a ratoang e neng simolohile United Kingdom a 1858 kapa 1863

Hangata ho kamehla amahanngoa le UK le Ireland
E atile fetisisa UK le linaheng tse neng li le likoloneng British bohareng ba lekholo la bo19 la lilemo, tse kang Afrika Borwa, Australia, New Zealand le Canada
United States haufinyane tjena ho ile ha feela li ile tsa amohela tsoang expatriates Canada le Irish, empa e ke se se sa tlwaelesegang pele le ka mor'a tsitsitseng sebeletsa
E ne e e ratoang kgolo le eena a Lihlekehleke Faroe ho tloha ka 1940, ha ho ne ho kenyelletsoa ke lule naheng British nakong ea ntoa ea bobeli ea Lefate.

Nelson Mandela Bay Metropolitan Municipality
Nelson Mandela Bay Municipality ke Metropolitan Masepala gofeta diporofense Kapa Bohlabela kamoka Afrika Borwa.
Sethaba se 1,152,115 , batho ba bulela Sethosa , Afrikaans  le Seisimane 
Municipal code ke NMA.
It is located on the shores of Algoa Bay in the Eastern Cape province, and comprises the city of Port Elizabeth, the nearby towns of Uitenhage and Despatch, and the surrounding rural area.
The name "Nelson Mandela Bay Municipality" was chosen to honour former President Nelson Mandela.

Mmasepala Setereke ta Overberg
Mmasepala Setereke ta Overberg ke district wa Kapa Bodikela.
Toropo kgolo kgolo ke Grabouw pop
21,593 in the Elgin Valley adjacent to the Hottentots-Holland on the north-western edge of the district
The municipal headquarters are located at Bredasdorp pop
12,749 in the southern part of the district
Other major towns are Swellendam pop
13,557 on the Breede River in the north-east, Caledon pop
10,650 in the western interior, and Hermanus pop
10,500 on the Atlantic coast.
The Overberg district is divided into four local municipalities, which are described in the following table.
E hleng mo City of Cape Town ka bodikela, Mmasepala Setereke ta Cape Winelands ka leboa, le Mmasepala Setereke ta Eden ka bohlabela.

Wattville
Wattville is a township south of Benoni in Ekurhuleni Metropolitan Municipality, Gauteng, South Africa
It was established in 1941, and by 1948, 400 houses were built on 34 hectares.
After 1948, building stopped as it was threatened with destruction
This was because it was considered too close to a white town
However, building continued in 1951 and by 1955 about 2,000 new houses had been erected.
The former African National Congress president Oliver Tambo lived here during the 1950s with his wife Adelaide
Mrs Tambo continued to serve the community and the local Anglican Church congregation, donating food parcels every year to the local senior citizens until she met her untimely death in 2008
She was buried next to her late husband in Wattville
A housing area was established in honour of the iconic couple, aptly named Tamboville with more than 800 families and still growing due to the influx of people into the township.
Katlehong
Katlehong ke township kgolo wa Ekurhuleni Metropolitan Municipality go feta diporofense Gauteng ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Katlehong e 35 km bohlabela la Johannesburg le borwa ka Germiston mô Thokoza le Vosloorus.

Bonaero Park
Bonaero Park ke motsesetoropo borwa bohlabela wa Kempton Park, Ekurhuleni Metropolitan Municipality go feta porofense Gauteng ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Toropo ke hleng ka "OR Tambo International Airport", airport e busy ka kgolo mô Afrika
Bonaero Park was built in the 1960s to house employees from the nearby military aircraft factory owned by Atlas Aircraft Corporation
In 1992 Atlas was absorbed into a new entity, Denel Aviation.
Company ta pedi ya difofane, "Comair" le "Kulula.com", ba nna le diheadoffice mô Bonaero Park.

Kleinbaai
Kleinbaai ke coastal toropo wa Overstrand, Mmasepala Setereke ta Overberg go feta Kapa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.

Sethaba se 176,899, e 76% ba bulela Setswana 
District code ke DC45.

Seat ya Namakwa ke Springbok

District code ke DC6.

St Faith's, KwaZulu Natala
St Faith's ke toropo wa Mmuôgaê wa Umzumbe go feta Mmasepala Setereke ta Ugu ka moka Afrika Borwa.
There are a number of settlements falling under St Faith's: uMqangqala, Nothinwta, Dweshula, Thaleni, Ngoleleni, Zitendeni, Siqhingini, Junction, Diphini, Maromeni and Ivethe
A taxi rank in Junction serves routes to Durban, Port Shepstone, Highflats and Ixopo
The route is also used by Ugu Transport buses.
Junction is the main part of St Faith's, it hosts a police station and health clinic near the St Faith's Community Hall
Maria Cross, Khakhamela, St Faith's, Impola are the primary schools, Indlelenhle Secondary and Mayiyana, Ntabalukhozi are the High Schools in St Faith's.
Mathulini
Mathulini ke toropo wa Mmuôgaê wa Umzumbe go feta Mmasepala Setereke ta Ugu ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Harding, KwaZulu Natala
Harding ke toropo wa Mmuôgaê wa uMuziwabantu go feta Mmasepala Setereke ta Ugu ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Harding was established as a military outpost following the British annexation of East Griqualand in 1874
Named after Sir Walter Harding  who in 1858 became the first Chief Justice in Natal.
Timber and dairy farming are the main economic activities
The abandoned 122 km narrow gauge Alfred County Railway used to serve the farming areas, linking Harding with Port Shepstone
Harding lies at the foot of the Ingeli Range, 34 km north-west of Izingolweni and 84 km north-west of Port Shepstone.

Vlieger ke village wa Mmuoselegae wa JB Marks go feta Mmasepala Setereke ta Dr Kenneth Kaunda wa profense Leboa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Kgakala
Kgakala ke township wa Leeudoringstad, Mmuoselegae wa Maquassi Hills go feta profense Leboa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Boskuil
Boskuil ke village nyane wa Mmuoselegae wa Maquassi Hills go feta diprofense Leboa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Trotsville
Trotsville ke township wa Wolmaransstad go feta Maquassi Hills, diprofense Leboa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Tswelelang
Tswelelang ke township wa Wolmaransstad, Maquassi Hills go feta diprofense Leboa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Rulaganyang
Rulaganyang ke township wa Witpoort, Maquassi Hills go feta diprofense Leboa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Matlwang
Matlwang ke village nyane bodikela wa Potchefstroom, go feta Mmasepala Setereke ta Dr Kenneth Kaunda, diprofense Leboa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Lindequesdrif
Lindequesdrif ke farm holdings botshabelo wa Potchefstroom, go feta Mmasepala Setereke ta Dr Kenneth Kaunda, profense Leboa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Hermannsburg
Hermannsburg ke village nyane wa Mmasepala Setereke ta uMzinyathi go feta porofense KwaZulu Natala ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Menkô
Menkô ke mohlare wa dikênywa.
Litchi
Litchi ke mohlare wa dikênywa.
Leimaniasis
Leimaniasis, gape e peletwa bjalo ka leimaniosis, ke bolweti bja go bakwa ke dipharasaete ta protozoan ta ditini ta "Leimania" gomme di phatlalatwa ke go longwa ga mehuta e mengwe ya dinthi ta santeng
Bolweti bo ka itlhagia ka mekgwa ye meraro: diwana, ta mamina, goba leimaniasis ya ditho ta ka gare
Mokgwa wa diwana o itlhagia ka diwana letlalong, mola mokgwa wa mamina o itlhagia ka diwana mo letlalong, molomong le ka nkong, gape mokgwa wa ditho ta ka gare o itlhagia ka dio mo letlalong gomme ka morago ya itlhagia ka letadi, disele te dikhubedu ta madi ta fase, le kgodio ya lebete le sebete.
Diphetelo go bathong di bakwa ke diupo ta go feta te 20 ta "Leimania"
Mabaka a kotsi a akareta bohloki, phepompe, go tlowa ga mehlare, le toropofato
Mehuta ka moka ye meraro e ka phekolwa ka go lebelela dipharasaete ka maekroskopo
Go tlaleleta, malweti a ditho ta ka gare a ka phekolwa ka diteko ta madi.
Leimaniasis e ka thibelwa ga nnyane ka go robala ka fase ga dinete ta go thelwa kalafi ya polaya khunkhwane Magato a mangwe a akareta sefothedi sa polaya khunkhwane go bolaya dinthi ta santeng le go alafa batho ka pela go thibela phatlalato ya go naba
Kalafi yeo e hlokegago e ya le gore bolweti bo hweditwe ka, diupo ta "Leimania", le mohuta wa phetelo
Dikalafi te dingwe ta kgonagalo te di diriwago go malweti a ditho ta ka gare di akareta liposomal amphoterisini B, tlhakanyo ya di-antimoniale ta pentabalente le paromomisini, le miltefosine
Go malweti a diwana, paromomisini, flukonazole goba pentamidine e ka thua.
Palo ya go feta dimilione te 12 ta batho ga bjale ba fetetwe dinageng te dingwe te 98
Palo ya go feta dimilione te 2 ta dikgetsi te dimpsha le magareng ga palo ya dikete te 20 le 50 ta mahu e twelela ngwaga ka ngwaga
Palo ya go feta dimilione te 200ta batho ka Asia, Afrika, Amerika Borwa le Bogare bja Amerika, le borwa bja Europa ba dula mafelong ao bolweti bjo bo tlwaelegilego
Mokgatlo wa Maphelo wa Lefase o hwedite phokoleto ya theko ya dikalafi te dingwe ta go alafa bolweti bjo
Bolweti bo ka twelela ka palo e nti go diphoofolo te dingwe, go akaretwa ta meno a polai le dikokoni.
Lephera
Lephera, gape le tsebega ka bolweti bja Hansen , ke phetelo ya lebaka le le telele ya go bakwa ke pakteria ya "Mycobacterium leprae" le "Mycobacterium lepromatosis"
Mathomong, diphetelo ga di be le diupo gomme go ba bjalo sebaka sa mengwaga ye 5 go ya go ye 20
Diupo te di twelelago di akareta digranuloma ta megalathika, mokgwa wa khemo, letlalo, le mahlo
Se se ka baka go palelwa ke go kwa bohloko le go felelwa ke ditho ta go oma kudu ka lebaka la go gobala leboelela goba phetelo ka lebaka la dintho ta go se lemogwe
Go felelwa ke maatla le go se bone gabotse go ka twelela.
Lephera le phatlalatwa magareng ga batho
Go dumelwa gore le ka twelela ka segohlola goba go kopana le seela sa ka nkong ya motho yoo a fetetwego
Lephera ganti le twelela magareng ga bahloki gape go dumelwa gore le fetetwa ka marothi a mokgwa wa khemo
Kgatlhanong le tumelo yeo e tlwaelegilego, ga le fetetwe kudu
Mehuta ye mebedi ya bolweti e theilwe ka palo ya dipakteria te di lego gona: paucibacillary le multibacillary
Mehuta ye mebedi e fapana ka palo ya mmala wa go se be botse, dipatso te di lego letlalong ta go hwa bogau, ka paucibacillary ya go ba le te hlano goba te nnyane le multibacillary ya go feta te hlano
Phekolo e kgonthieditwe ka go hweta esiti-ya lebelo ya bacilli ka biopsy ya letlalo goba go lekola DNA ka go diria ketwana ya phetogo ya polymerase.
Lephera le a alafega ka kalafi yeo e tsebegago ka multidrug therapy 
Kalafi ya lephera la paucibacillary e ka dikalafi ta dapsone le rifampicin sebaka sa dikgwedi te tshela
Kalafi ya lephera la multibacillary e na le rifampicin, dapsone, le clofazimine sebaka sa dikgwedi te 12
Dikalafi te di fiwa mphiwafela ke ba Mokgatlo wa Maphelo wa Lefase
Mehuta ye mengwe ya di-antibiotiki e ka diriwa
Ka 2012 lefaseng ka bophara, palo ya dikgetsi ta bolweti bja kalafi ya go se fole bja lephera e be e le 189,000 palo ya ka fase ga dimilione te 5.2 million mengwageng ya bo-1980
Palo e mpsha ya dikgetsi e be e le 230,000
Dikgetsi te mpsha di twelete dinageng te 16, gomme India e balwa goba le palo ya go feta palogare
Mengwaga ye 20 ya go feta, palo ya dimilione te 16 ta batho lefaseng ka bophara ba alafilwe lephera mme ba fodile
Palo ya dikgetsi ta go feta 200 di begwa ngwaga ka ngwaga ka United States.
Lephera le amile batho sebaka sa diketekete ta mengwaga
Bolweti bjo bo hwedite leina la lona go twa go lentu la se-Latinla "lepra", leo le tlhaloago gore "legapi", mola leina la "bolweti bja Hansen" le theilwe ka morago ka ngaka Gerhard Armauer Hansen
Go aroganya batho ka go ba bea ka dikoloni ta lephera go sa nte go sa twelela mafelong a mangwe bjalo ka India, Thaena, le Afrika
Le ge go le bjale, dikoloni te dinti di tswaletwe ka ge lephera le se sa fetela kudu
Mmamodula wa selegae o amantwe le lephera ka histori e nti, gomme se se twelapele gore batho ba bege ka bo bona le go hweta kalafo ya ka pela
Batho ba bangwe ba nagana gore lentu le lephera le kwea bohloko, gomme ba rata ge go ka diriwa mmolelwana "batho ba go fetelwa ke lephera"
Letati la Lephera la Lefase le thomilwe ka 1954 go phatlalata tsebo go bao ba angwago ke lephera.
Onkhocerciasis
Onkhoseriasis, yeo gape e tsebegago bjalo ka noka ya foufato le bolweti bja Robles, ke bolweti bja go bakwa ke phetelo ya seboko sa pharasaete sa "Onkhocerca volvulus"
Dika ta bolweti di akareta go hlohlona go oro, go ruruga ka gare ga letlalo, le go foufala
Ke sehlodi sa bobedi sa go tlwaelega sa go baka bofofu ka lebaka la phetelo, ka morago ga trakhoma.
Seboko sa pharasaete se phatlalatwa ka go longwa ke nthi e ntsho ya "mohuta wa" Simulium
Ka tlwaelo o ka longwa ganti pele phetelo e twelela
Dinthi te di dula kgauswi le dinoka, bjale ka ge leina la bolweti le itlhalosa
Ge seboko se le ka gare ga motho, se dira sebokwana seo se hwetago tsela ya go tsenelela letlalong
Gomme go tloga mo se fetela nthi e ntsho e latelago yeo e ka lomago motho
Go na le mekgwa e mmalwa ya go dira phekolo go akaretwa: go bea biopsy ya letlalo ka gare ga saline ya go tlwaelega le go lebelela sebokwana se etwa, go lebelela ka gare ga leihlo go lekola seboko le go lebelela go ruruga ga seboko se segolo ka gare ga letlalo.
Ga go na kenti kgatlhanong le bolweti bjo
Thibelo e ka dirwa fela ka go efoga go longwa ke dinthi
Se se ka akareta thomio ya dikoba dikhunkhwane le diaparo ta maleba
Maitekelo a mangwe a akareta phokoto ya palo ya dinthi ka go fothela dipolaya khunkhwane
Maitekelo a go fedia bolweti ka go alafa dihlopha ka moka ta batho ga bedi ka ngwaga a twelapele mafelong a mmalwa lefaseng ka bophara
Kalafo ya bao ba fetetwego e dirwa ka kalafi ya ivermectin dikgwedi te dingwe le te dingwe te tshela go ya go te lesomepedi
Kalafi ye e bolaya sebokwana efela e sego diboko te dikgolo
Kalafi ya doxycycline, yeo e bolayago ya go amanywa le pakteria yeo e bitwago "Wolbachia", e bonagala e okobata diboko gomme e digelwa ke babangwe
Go tloa go ruruga ka fase ga letlalo ka puo go ka dirwa.
Palo ya dimilione te 17 go ya go 25 ba fetetwe ka foufalo ya noka, ka tekanyeto ya dimilione te 0.8 ta batho ba go se sa bona botse
Diphetelo te dinti di twelela ka sub-Saharan Afrika, le ge ele gore dikgetsi di begilwe ka Yemen le mafelo ao a kgetholotwego Bogare le Borwa bja Amerika
Ka 1915, ngaka Rodolfo Robles mathomong o ile a tswalanya seboko le bolweti bja mahlo
E ngwadiitwe ke Mokgatlo wa Maphelo wa Lefase bjalo ka bolweti bja go hlokomologwa bja molatati.
Bolweti bja Rabies
Bolweti bja Rabies ke bja phetelo ya go baka go ruruga ga bjoko go batho le diphoofolo ta madi a-borutho
Diupo ta ka pela di akareta letadi le go hlabahlabega mo e twelelago gona
Diupo te di latelwa ke enngwe goba te mmalwa ta diupo te di latelago: mesepelo ya go laeta booro, lethabo la go se laolege, bofiega bja meetse, go palelwa ke go uthia ditho ta mmele, go gakanega, le go idibala
Morago ga ge diupo di twelete, bolweti bja rabies bo tla be bo ete bo laeta lehu
Nako ya magareng ga go swarwa ke bolweti le go thoma ga diupo ganti ke sebaka sa kgwedi e tee go ya go te tharo
Le ge go le bjale, sebaka se se ka fapana go tloga go sebaka sa ka fase ga beke e tee go ya go ngwaga o tee
Sebaka sa nako se ya le bokgole bjoo baerase e sepelago ka gona go fihlelela bogare bja tsela ya megalathika.
Bolweti bja rabies bo fetela batho go twa diphoofolong
Bolweti bja rabies bo ka fetela ge phoofolo yeo e fetetwego e ka ngwapa goba ya loma phoofolo ye nngwe goba motho
Mare a phoofolo yeo e fetetwego a ka feteta bolweti bja rabies ge eba mare a kgomana le lera la phoofolo goba motho
Dikgetsi te dinti ta bolweti bja rabies mo bathong di bakilwe ke go longwa ke mpa
Dikgetsi ta go feta 99% ta bolweti bja rabies mo dinageng teo dimpa di nago le rabies di bakilwe ke go longwa ke mpa
Ka Amerika, go longwa ke mmankgagane ke mothopo o tlwaelegilego wa phetelo ya bolweti bja rabies mo bathong, gomme dikgetsi ta ka fase ga 5% ke ta dimpa
Dikokoni ganti ga ke di fetelwa ke bolweti bja rabies
Baerase ya bolweti bja rabies e kitimela ka bjokong ka go latela thoga thogo ya peripheral
Bolweti bo ka phekolwa fela ka morago ga ge diupo di thomile.
Mananeo a taolo ya diphoofolo le kento a fokodite dikotsi ta bolweti bja rabies dimpeng deleteng te mmalwa lefaseng
Go thontia batho pele ba ka fetelwa go a eletwa go bao ba lego kotsing e kgolo
Dihlopha te di lego kotsing e kgolo di akareta batho bao ba omago ka dimmankgagane goba bao ba dulago sebaka se se telele mafelong a lefase ao bolweti bja rabies bo tlwaelegilego
Go batho bao ba etego ba utullote bolweti bja rabies, kenti ya rabies le ka nako te dingwe immunoglobulin ya rabies e ka thua go thibela bolweti ge eba motho o hweta kalafi pele diupo ta bolweti bja rabies di twelela
Go hlatswa go longwa goba mongwapo metsotso ye 14 ka sesepe le meetse, povidone iodine, goba dihlwekii ka ge di ka bolaya baerase gape go bonagala e ke go ka thua thibelo ya phetelo ya bolweti bja rabies
Ke batho ba mmalwa fela bao ba phologilego phetelo ya bolweti bja rabies morago ga go laeta diupo
Phologo ye e diregile ka kalafi e tseneletego yeo e tsebagalago ka prothokholo ya Milwaukee .
Kenti ya bolweti bja rabies ke kenti yeo e diriwago go thibela bolweti bja rabies
Go na le te dingwe te mmalwa te di bolokegilego gape te di omago gabotse
Di ka diriwa go thibela bolweti bja rabies pele gape sebaka se se telele morago ga go hweta baerase ka go longwa ke mpa goba mmankgagane
Thontio yeo e twelelago e tea sebaka morago ga ditose te tharo
Ganti e fiwa ka tlhabelo ka gare ga letlalo goba thika
Morago ga phetelo kenti e diriwa mmogo le immunoglobulin ya bolweti bja rabies
Go tloga go eletwa gore bao ba lego kotsing e kgolo ya go ka fetelwa ba entwe pele ba ka fetelwa
Dikenti di oma botse mo bathong le diphoofolo te dingwe
Go thontia dimpa go thua kudu go thibela bolweti mo bathong.
Dimilione ta batho lefaseng ka bophara ba entilwe gomme go lekanyeditwe gore se se boloka maphelo a batho ba 250,000 ka ngwaga
Se se ka diriwa ka polokego go dihlopha ka moka ta mengwaga
Palo ya dipersente ta go feta 35 go ya go 45 ta batho ba hweta bohwibidu le go kwa bohloko ga nnyane mo ba tlhabetwego gona
Palo ya dipersente ta go feta 5 go ya go 15 ta batho ba ka ba le letadi, ba opa ke hlogo, goba ba kwa ba nyaka go hlata
Morago ga go fetelwa ke bolweti bja rabies ga go na ditlamorago ta kgatlhano ya thomio ya yona
Dikenti te dinti ga di na thiomersal
Dikenti te di dirilwego ka thiu ya mogalathika di a diriwa dinageng te mmalwa, ganti ka Asia, Latin Amerika, gomme ga di ome gabotse kudu ebile di na le ditlamorago te dinti
Ka fao thomio ya tona ga e eleletwe ke ba Mokgatlo wa Maphelo wa Lefase.
Theko ya lebenkeleng e magareng ga 44 le 78 USD ya kalafi go tloga ka 2014
Ka United States theko ya kalafi ya bolweti bja rabies e feta 750 USD.
Bolweti bja rabies bo baka palo ya mahu a go feta 26,000 go ya go 55,000 lefaseng ka bophara ka ngwaga
Palo ya go feta 95% ya mahu ao a diragala ka Asia le Afrika
Bolweti bja rabies bo hwetagala dinageng ta go feta 150 le dikontinente ka moka eupa le ka Antarktika
Batho ba go feta dimilione te 3 ba dula dileteng ta lefase moo bolweti bja rabies bo hwetagalago
Bonti bja Europa le Australia, bolweti bja rabies bo hwetagala fela go dimmankgagane
Dithaba ta ditlhakatlhaka te dinti te di nnyane ga di na bolweti bja rabies le ga tee.
Schistosomiasis
Schistosomiasis, gape e bitwa letadi la kgopa, ke bolweti bja go bakwa ke pharasaete ya diboko ta go patlama te di bitwago di-schistosome
Tshepeto ya moroto goba mala di ka fetelwa
Maswao le diupo di ka akareta bohloko dimpeng, lethologo, mantle a go ba le madi, goba madi ka gare ga moroto
Batho bao ba fetetwego sebaka se se telele ba ka itemogela tshenyego ya sebete, go se sa oma ga dipshio, go se sa kgona go belega, goba kankere ya sebudula
Mo baneng, e ka baka go se gole botse le bothata bja go ithuta.
Bolweti bo phatlalatwa ka go kgoma meetse a go hlweka a go thilafatwa ke dipharasaete
Dipharasaete te di lokollwa go twa go dikgopa ta meetse a go hlweka
Bolweti bjo bo tlwaelegile magareng ga bana bao ba lego go dinaga te di twetego pele ka ge ba rata go raloka ka gare ga meetse a go thilafatwa
Dihlopha te dingwe te di lego kotsing di akareta balemi, barei ba dihlapi, le batho bao ba diriago meetse a go se hlweke tati ka tati
Ke ya sehlopha sa diphetelo ta helminth
Phekolo e dirwa ka go hweta mae a pharasaete ka gare ga moroto goba mantle a motho
E ka kgonthiiwa ka go hweta dilwantha mmele kgatlhanong le bolweti ka gare ga madi.
Mekgwa ya go thibela bolweti e akareta kaonafato ya phihlelelo ya meetse a go hlweka le go fokota palo ya dikgopa
Mafelong ao bolweti bo tlwaelegilego, kalafi ya praziquantel e ka fiwa ga tee ka ngwaga go sehlopha ka moka
Se se dirwa go fokota palo ya batho bao ba fetetwego le, ditla morago, ta phatlalato ya bolweti
Praziquantel gape ke kalafi e eletwago ke ba Mokgatlo wa Maphelo wa Lefase  go bao go tsebegago gore ba fetetwe.
Schistosomiasis e amile palo ya go nyaka go lekana le dimilione te 210 lefaseng ka bophara ka 2012
Tekanyeto ya palo ya batho ba 12,000 go ya go 200,000 ba hlokofala ka baka la yona ngwaga ka ngwaga
Bolweti bjo ganti bo hwetagala ka Afrika, le Asia gape ka Borwa bja Amerika
Palo ya batho ba go feta dimilione te 700, go dinaga ta go feta te 70, ba dula mafelong ao bolweti bjo bo tlwaelegilego
Go dinaga ta melatati, schistosomiasis ke ya bobedi go malaria magareng ga malweti a dipharasaete a go ama ekonomi ka tsela e kgolo
Schistosomiasis e lenaneong lamalweti a melatati a go hlokomologwa.
Letadi la Zika
Letadi la Zika  ke bolweti bja go bakwa ke baerase ya Zika
Dikgetsi te dinti ga di na diupo, eupa ge di le gona ganti di ba magareng gomme di swana le ta letadi la dengue
Diupo di ka akareta letadi, mahlo a go hwibila, bohloko bja lelokollo, go opwa ke hlogo, le diwana ta maculopapular .Ka kakareto diupo di ka bonagala sebaka sa ka fase ga matati a upa
Ga se nke bo bake dipego ta mahu dikgatong ta mathomo ta phetelo
Phetelo e tswalanywa le Guillain–Barré syndrome .
Letadi la Zika ganti le phatlalatwa ka go longwa ke menang ya "mohuta wa" Aedes
Gape e ka ba ya fetelwa ka thobalano go twa go monna go ya go balekani ba gagwe ba thobalano gape e ka fetetwa kudu ka phatlalalo ka go fana ka madi
Diphetelo go basadi bao ba imilego di ka fetela ngwana gomme di ka baka hlokofalo ya ngwana ka mpeng le microcephaly
Diphekolo di dirwa ka diteko ta madi, moroto, goba mare go lekola go ba gona ga baerase ya Zika ya RNA ge motho a lwala.
Thibelo e akareta phokoto ya go longwa ke menang mafelong ao bolweti bo twelelago le tirio ya maleba ya dikhontomo
Maitekelo a go thibela go longwa a akareta thomio ya dikoba menang, go khupeta mmele ka moka ka diaparo, dinete ta menang, le phedio ya meetse a go ema sebaka moo menang e tswalago gona
Ga go na kentie diriwago
Baomi ba ta maphelo ba eleta gore basadi bao ba lego mafelong ao a amegilwego ke 2015–16 go wa ga Zika ba gopole go se ime gomme bao ba imilego ba se ke ba etela dinaga teo
Mola go se nago kalafi e iteng, paracetamol  e ka thua ka diupo
Go robatwa bookelong ganti ga go hlokege.
Baerase yeo e bakago bolweti e ile ya aroganywa la mathomo ka 1947
Go ngwala ga go wa la mathomo ga bolweti magareng ga batho go twelete ka 2007 ka Federated States ya Micronesia
Bolweti bo be bo twelela dileteng te masomepedi ta Amerika
Gape go tsebega bo twelela gape ka Afrika, Asia, le Pacifiki
Ka lebaka la go wa ga bolweti go go thomilego ka Brazil ka 2015, ba Mokgatlo wa Maphelo wa Lefase ba bo begile bjalo ka Public Health Emergency of International Concern ka Febereware 2016.
Townview, Mooi River
Townview ke township wa Mooi River mo Mmasepala Setereke ta uMgungundlovu go feta KwaZulu Natala ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Bruntville
Bruntville ke township wa Mooi River mo Mmasepala Setereke ta uMgungundlovu go feta KwaZulu Natala ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Dukathole
Dukathole ke township wa Aliwal North mo Mmasepala Setereke ta Joe Gqabi go feta porofense Kapa Bohlabela  ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Township e 163 km lebowa la Queenstown le 206 km borwa la Bloemfontein.
Sonwabile
Sonwabile ke township wa Maclear go feta Mmasepala Setereke ta Joe Gqabi wa porofense Kapa Bohlabela  ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Township e 216km lebowa bohlabela la Queenstown le 239km bohlabela la Aliwal North.
Kwanokuthula
Kwanokuthula ke black African township wa Plettenberg Bay, toropo wa Bitou Mmusogae go feta Kapa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Bossiesgerf
Bossiesgerf ke black settlement hleng wa Plettenberg Bay, toropo wa Bitou Mmusogae go feta Kapa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
New Horizons, Plett
New Horizons ke mainly coloured township wa Plettenberg Bay, toropo wa Bitou Mmusogae go feta Kapa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Mmuôgaê wa :Khara Hais
Mmuôgaê wa :Khara Hais ke mmasepala go feta Mmasepala Setereke ta ZF Mgcawu wa diporofense Kapa Leboa ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Toropo kgolo kgolo ya Mmuôgaê wa :Khara Hais ke Upington
Israel
Israel ke naga lefasaneng la Asia.
Nkqubela
Nkqubela ke township ya Robertson, Langeberg Mmusogae, Cape Winelands go feta Kapa Bodikela, ka moka Afrika Borwa.
ENduli
eNduli ke township bohlabela ya Ceres, Witzenberg Mmusogae, Cape Winelands go feta Kapa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Bella Vista
Bella Vista ke township leboa ya Ceres, Witzenberg Mmusogae, Cape Winelands go feta Kapa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Langrug
Langrug ke township hleng la toropo Franschhoek, Mmasepala Setereke ta Cape Winelands go feta Kapa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Groendal
Groendal ke township ya Bammala, hleng la toropo Franschhoek, Mmasepala Setereke ta Cape Winelands go feta Kapa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Montana, Kapa Bodikela
Montana ke township wa Bammala, hleng la toropo Wolseley, Witzenberg, Mmasepala Setereke ta Cape Winelands go feta Kapa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Pine Valley
Pine Valley ke township hleng la Wolseley, toropo wa Witzenberg, Mmasepala Setereke ta Cape Winelands go feta Kapa Bodikela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
1727
1727  ebile ngwaga wa go thoma ka Laboraro, ngwaga wa boseswai ngwagengsome wa 1720s, ngwaga wa bomasomepedi upa ngwagengkgolo wa Ngwagakgolo 18, le ngwaga wa bomakgolo upa masomepedi upa ngwagengkete wa Ngwagakete 2.
1643
1643  ebile ngwaga wa go thoma ka Labone, ngwaga wa bone ngwagengsome wa 1640s, ngwaga wa bomasomenne tharo ngwagengkgolo wa Ngwagakgolo 17, le ngwaga wa bomakgolo tshela masomenne tharo ngwagengkete wa Ngwagakete 2.
Paromomisini
Paromomisini is a aminoglycoside antibiotic, first isolated from "Streptomyces krestomuceticus" in the 1950s
It was discovered by Parke Davis .
It is on the World Health Organization's  List of Essential Medicines, a list of the most important medication needed in a basic health system.
Flukonazole
Flukonazole is an antifungal medication that is given either by mouth or intravenously
It is used to treat a variety of fungal infections, especially "Candida" infections of the vagina, mouth, throat, and bloodstream.
It is on the World Health Organization's  List of Essential Medicines, a list of the most important medication needed in a basic health system.
Simondium
Simondium ke hamlet 8 km borwa ya Paarl go feta Kapa Bodikela.
It was named after Pierre Simond , Huguenot minister at the Cape.
Moruba wa sekgowa
Moruba wa sekgowa  ke papadi, batho ba ralôkia tafôlêng.
Nile
Nile ke noka kgolokgolo wa Afrika.
Noka
Noka ke "river" ka Seisimane.
Thaba
Thaba ke "mountain" ka Seisimane.
Naga
Naga  ke sebaka se e tsejoa e le mokhatlo oa ikemeteng a jeokrafi lipolotiki
Naga ka 'na ba e ikemeteng ipusang e kapa e mong e lula puo e' ngoe, e le go arola bao e eng a bobusi kapa pele e neng e le 'musi ea lipolitiki kapa ea sebakeng libopeho te amanang le re behela ea batho ba neng ikemeteng kapa ka tela e fapaneng amahanngoang le go sebelisoa litsobotsi buella lipolitiki
Go sa tsotellehe gore thutafase meleng, a ea kajeno amohela matjhabeng tlhaloso ea molao joalokaha hlalosoa ke Selekane sa Lichaba ka 1937 'me a se tiisa ke Machaba a Kopaneng ka 1945, moagi oa naga e e ka tlaa go ikoetlia ikemeteng ea taolo tabeng ea molao.
Ka linako te ling linaheng te lentsoe e sebelisoa go fetiseta ka bobedi go ipusang le go mekhatlo e meng ea lipolitiki, ga a nte a linako te ling le bolela feela go e re
Ka mohlala, "CIA World Factbook" sebelia lentsoe ta lona "Country: bolela "timo go bolela" te ngata ta dependencies, libakeng te bobusing ba khethehileng, lihlekehleke te se nang baahi, 'me mekhatlo ea te ling go phaella go linaheng te tlwaelo kapa o bolela ikemeteng."
Sekgwa
Sekgwa ke sebakeng se segolo ba naga koahetsoeng ka lifate kapa tse ling tse woody limela
Ba makholo a litlhaloso tobileng haholoanyane tsa moru li sebelisoa go pholletsa le lefate, se nang lintho tse kang sefate segokanyipalo, bophahamo sefate, go sebelisa mobu, e eme ka molao me mosebetsi tlholeho
Go e ka go pharaletseng sebelisoa United Nations Lijo le Temo Organization tlhaloso, meru koahela hektare bilione tse nè  kapa hoo e ka bang karolo ea 30 lekholong ea sebaka naheng ea lefate go ea ka 2006.
Meru ke muso o hlaheletseng ta lefae bottler ea lefae me ba aba ka mose wa lefae
Meru ikarabella ka 75% ea feteletseng tlhahiso e ka sehloohong ea biosphere lefae, me e na le 80% ea limela biomass ea lefae.
Orange River
Orange River  ke noka letelele kgolo wa Afrika Borwa.
Vaal River
Vaal River  ke yona ekgolo noka fitisisa ka Makala a dinoka tse telang Orange River mô Afrika Borwa.
Toropokgolo
Toropokgolo ke main toropo wa naga, kane wa masipala.
Mmuôgaê wa Walter Sisulu
Mmuôselegae wa Walter Sisulu ke mmuôselegaê go feta Mmasepala Setereke ta Joe Gqabi wa porofense Kapa Bohlabela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Motse-kgolo ya Walter Sisulu ke Aliwal North.
Metse ya mmuôselegaê ke:
Dinoka wa mmuôselegaê:
Mmuôselegae wa Enoch Mgijima
Mmuôselegae wa Enoch Mgijima ke mmasepala go feta Mmasepala Setereke ta Chris Hani wa porofense Kapa Bohlabela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Formed after the merger of Lukhanji Mmusogae, Tsolwana Mmusogae and Inkwanca Mmusogae on 8 August 2016.
Mmuôgaê wa Raymond Mhlaba
Mmuôgaê wa Raymond Mhlaba ke mmusogae go feta Mmasepala Setereke ta Amathole wa porofense Kapa Bohlabela ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Formed after the merger of Nkonkobe Mmusogae and Nxuba Mmusogae
Toropokgolo wa Raymond Mhlaba ke Fort Beaufort.
Toropo wa mmasepala:
Cathay Pacific
Cathay Pacific Limited ke lifofane tsoang Hong Kong
E tsamaisa batho le thepa kapa go e ka godimo go 120 metse lefate ka bophara
Botlaaseng ya yona e kgolo kapa khubu ke ka Hong Kong International Airport.
Ke e 'ngoe ea Airlines tse teletseng lefateng go fumana tse hlano stjernerangering tsoang Skytrax
E swarwile "Lifofane ta Ngwaga" khau tsoang Skytrax ka 2003, 2005 le 2009
Morali'abo rona e eona lifofane e Dragonair e leng o sebeletsa celow Thaena linaheng le Asia.
Etihad Airways
Etihad Airways ke lifofane ye kgolo wa United Arab Emirates
E ileng ba bptjoa ka molao-taelo ya borena ka July 2003
E ile ea tomile go fofa bapalami ba nkang ka November 2003
Abu Dhabi, toropokgolo wa United Arab Emirates, ke khubu ya lifofane kapa botlaaseng ba buuoe.
Etihad Airways se fofa libakeng 63 mô dinageng te 42.
Emirates
Emirates ke lifofane ka naga ya Dubai, United Arab Emirates 
Khampani e thehiloe a May 1985 ke muso wa UAE.
Emirates o bontitse sebeletsa kgolo e potlakileng ka kgolo
Sefofane fana a mangata a Bohabela bo Gare, Asia, Europa, Afrika, India, Oceania le Amerika Leboa
Ka 25 October 1985 li ile tsa phethile vuelos pele oa go India le Pakistan
Pakeng ta 1987 le bo-1990 ba ile Asia le Europe 'mapeng
Emirates ile ea e-batsholadisereng ea SriLankan Airlines ka la 1 April 1998
Go tloha ka la 1 October 2015, Emirates fofelang habeli letsatsi le letati bao e seng setopong tsoang Dubai go Amsterdam le Brussels Airport
E thepa likarolo ta Emirates chesang Emirates SkyCargo.
Kepe boo lapeng ke Dubai International Airport wa Dubai
Go tloha ka 20 June 2010 Emirates e boetse e sebelisa boema-fofane ta ncha Dubai: Al Maktoum International Airport
Letating leo o ile a fihla sefofane EK9883, e leng thepa balega Hong Kong.
Singapore Airlines
Singapore Airlines Limited   ke folakha mojari ya Singapore le le 5-star lefofane
Singapore Airlines sebetsang ho tloha setsi sa se ka Airport Singapore Changi lula a boteng matla a Asia Borwa-bochabela, Asia Bochabela, Asia Borwa le "Kangaroo Route" limmaraka.
Boeing 747-8
Boeing 747-8 ke sefofane se seholo sa lifofane se tsamaisoang ke Boeing Commercial Airplanes
E phatlalalitsoeng ka molao ka 2005, 747-8 ke moloko oa boraro oa Boeing 747, o nang le fuselage e telele, mapheo a tsosolositsoeng le bokhoni bo ntlafetseng
E 747-8 ke phetolelo e kholo ka ho fetisisa ea 747, sefofane se seholo ka ho fetisisa sa khoebo se hahiloeng United States, le sefofane se selelele ka ho fetisisa sa baeti lefateng.
Mantsoe a 747-8 a nyeheloa ka mefuta e 'meli e meholo e kholo: bapalami ba 747-8 ba Intercontinental le mofolisi oa 747-8 bakeng sa thepa.Mantsoe a 747-8F a pele a ile a baleha ka la 8 February, 2010, le 747-8 Intercontinental ka morao ho la 20 Mphalane 2011
Ho tsamaisoa ha sefofane sa pele sa sefofane se ile sa etsahala ka October 2011 'me mokhoa oa bapalami o qalile ho tsamaisoa ka 2012
Ho tloha ka June 2016 , o netefalitse litaelo tsa hore 747-8 e kakaretso ea 125, e nang le 74 ea sebopeho sa freighter, le 51 ea bapalami ba phetolelo.
Sespan
Sespan ke polelo yeo setlogo sa yona e lego Spain.
Mmuôgaê wa Ray Nkonyeni
Mmuôgaê wa Ray Nkonyeni ke  mmasepala go feta Mmasepala Setereke ta Ugu ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Boeing 737
Sefofane ta Boeing 737 ke short to mediumrange twinjet narrow-body airliner
Seo qalong se neng pele e le khutsoanyane, tlaasana litenyehelo lefahla-enjene le sefofane tsoa Boeing a 707 le 727, e 737 e ntshetswa pele lelapeng la leshome dikai tsa baeti le maemong ana ho tloha bapalami ba nkang 85 ho 215
737 e Boeing feela moqotetsane-'mele sefofane seo a tlhahiso, ka 737 Next Generation  variants gajoale o e ntse e gahoa
Production o boetse o tomile ka botjha engined le redesigned 737 MAX, e leng e behiloeng ka ho kenela tebeletso ea ka 2017.
Lufthansa
Deutsche Lufthansa AG  tsejoang Lufthansa ke kgolo ka go fetisisa Jeremane lifofane, ga go kopantswe le ka tiasa yona yona, le e lifofane kgolo ka go fetisisa Europe, ka bobeli ya ka dipehelo ta bapalami ba nkang etsoa le likepe bogolo
It operates services to 18 domestic destinations and 197 international destinations in 78 countries across Afrika, Amerika, Asia le Europe, sebelisa likepe tse baetsi ba lifofane go feta 260
Lufthansa ke e mong oa litho te hlano ta Star Alliance, ea li hulang pele sefofane selekane, thehoa ka 1997.
Ntle go moo Airlines tsa lona tsa baeti Austria Airlines, Switzerland International Air Lines, le Eurowings go akarelletsa Germanwings
Kopantswe le ka tiasa yona ba eona, sehlopha na holim baetsi ba lifofane 615, etsa hore ho e' ngoe ea kgolo ka go fetisisa fleets baeti lifofane lefateng
Ka 2014, sehlopha etsoa tse ka godimo go nka bapalami ba limilione tse 106.
Boeing 707
Boeing 707 ke bogareng ba bo-e bogolo bo lekaneng, nako e telele, e moqotetsane-'mele li' ne enjene jete sefofane seo hahiloeng ke Boeing Commercial lifofane tloha ka 1958 go 1979
Lebitso la eona ka tloaelo go phatlalatsa e le "seven oh seven"
Liphetolelong tsa baetsi ba lifofane ba na le bokgoni ba go tloha bapalami ba nkang 140 ho 219 le mefuta e fapaneng ya 2.500 go 5.750 lik'hilomithara tse nautical 
4
707 e ile ntshetswa pele ho tloha Boeing 367-80, mochine o sa jete sa ea pele ea tlisoa ka lifofane ka 1954
A kholoanyane fuselage a cross-karolo ya le diphetolo tse ling fella ka hore ebe qalong-tlhahiso 707-120, tsamaisoa ka Pratt  Whitney JT3C dienjini turbojet, e leng ea pele sefofane mabapi le 20 December 1957
Pan American World Airways e tomile e 707 tebeletso ea hae mabapi le 26 October 1958
Hamorao derivatives akarelletsa shortened nako e telele 707-138 le 707-320 otlolla, tseo ka bobeli li kenela tebeletso ka 1959
a short- tse nyenyane tse fapaneng tsena lia fetana, e 720, e ne e hlahiswa ka 1960
The 707-420, e leng phetolelo ea 707 otlolla le Rolls-Royce Conway turbofans, debuted a 1960, ga a ntse a Pratt  Whitney JT3D turbofans debuted ka 707-120B le 707-320B dikai ka 1961 le ka 1962, ka go latellana.
Boeing 727
Boeing 727 ke sefofane bo-bogolo e moqotetsane-'mele a mararo enjene go lifofane tse kgolo hahiloeng ke Boeing Commercial Airplanes tsoang ya 1960 mathoasong a lekgolo go 1984
1 Go ka phetha bapalami ba nkang 149 ho tse 189' me dikai hamorao ka fofa go fihlela ho 2.700 nautical lik'hilomithara tse  sa khaotse
O ne a rerile bakeng sa baratos khutoanyane le tse mahareng bolelele, e 727 ka sebelisa lifofane tse batlang e le khutoanyane ea boema-fofaneng le menyenyane
E na Pratt  Whitney JT8D dienjini tse tharo tse ka tlase go T-mohatla, e mong ka lehlakoreng ka leng la fuselage morao le setsi enjene e amahanya go pholletsa e S-difapho go lesoba e botlaaseng
The 727 e Boeing feela hut-lifofane tse kgolo.
The 727 latela 707, e leng quad-jete sefofane seo, leo ka arolelanang ka holimo fuselage a cross-karolo ya ea sona le cockpit boqapi ba bona
The 727-100 la pele sefofane ka February 1963 le kenela tebeletso le Eastern Air Lines ka February 1964 ea otlolla 727-200 sefofane ka July 1967 le kenela tebeletso le ka leboea-bochabela Airlines hore December
The 727 e ile ea e ka sehloohong ea marangrang Airlines 'tsamaea ka tsela efe e ruuoang le ne le boetse le sebelisoa mabapi le litsela tse ling tse short- le seaplane e telele linaheng tsa machaba
Mopalami, freighter, le e fetohang liphetolelong tsa 727 go ile ha hahoa.
The 727 e ile ka kgolo hlahisoang ho kena 1970s ea a ho qetela 727 e ile ea phethoa ka 1984
Go tloha ka July 2013, kakaretso ea batho ba 109 Boeing 727s  ba ne ba le tebeletso ea likhoele tsa khoebo le 34 Airlines
Le melao ea tsamaiso Airport lerata li ile sa etsa hore 727s ho a hlomelloa le lebokosana le khutso e kgolo.
Airbus A300
Sefofane sa Airbus A300 ke sefofane se kgolo, ba aga mo Jeremane, Fora, le Spain ka moka Europa.
Airbus A380
Sefofane sa Airbus A380 ke sefofane se kgolokgolo, ba aga mo Jeremane, Fora, le Spain ka moka Europa.
Boeing 777
Boeing 777 ke lelapa la lifofane tse tsamaeang ka nako e telele tse nang le lifofane tse ngata tse entsoeng ka lifofane tse entsoeng ka bobeli le tse entsoeng ke Boeing Commercial Airplanes
Ke twinjet e kholo ka ho fetisisa lefats'eng 'me e na le matla a tloaelehileng a bolulo bakeng sa bapalami ba 314 ho ea ho 451, e nang le lik'hilomithara tse 5 235 ho ea ho tse 9 500 tse nang le marulelo a mararo .
Lintho tse khethollang ka tloaelo li bitsoa "Triple Seven", likarolo tsa eona tse khethollang li na le li-drive tse kholo ka ho fetisisa tsa turbofan tsa sefofane leha e le sefe, mabili a teletseng ka thepa e ka sehloohong ea ho fihla, sehlopha se seholo sa sefate sa fuselage, le sefate sa mohatla
E thehiloe ka lipuisano le lifofane tse kholo tse robeli, 777 e ne e etselitsoe ho nka lifofane tsa khale tsa batho ba bangata le borokho ba phapang pakeng tsa boeing ea 767 le 747
Joaloka sefofane sa pele sa Boeing se tsamaeang le sefofane, se na le taolo ea motlakase
E ne e boetse e le sefofane sa pele sa khoebo se lokelang ho etsoa ka ho feletseng ka moqapi oa li-computer.
Air France
Air France, stylized as AIRFRANCE, is the French flag carrier headquartered in Tremblay-en-France, 
It is a subsidiary of the Air France–KLM Group and a founding member of the SkyTeam global airline alliance
As of 2013 Air France serves 36 destinations in France and operates worldwide scheduled passenger and cargo services to 168 destinations in 93 countries  and also carried 46,803,000 passengers in 2015.
Air France, stylized joalokaha AIRFRANCE, ke Fora folakha headquartered a Tremblay-en-France, 
Ke ka tlaasana ea Air France–KLM Group le setho mothehi oa SkyTeam lifofane oa lefate lohle selekane
Joalokaha sa 2013 Air France sebeletsa 36 celow Fora le sebetsang lefateng ka bophara ho lokiselitsoe baeti le thepa lits'ebeletso ho 168 celow linaheng 93  'me e boetse etsoa bapalami ba nkang 46.803.000 ka 2015.
Qantas
Qantas  is the flag carrier airline of Australia and its largest airline by fleet size, international flights and international destinations
It is the third oldest airline in the world, after KLM and Avianca having been founded in November 1920 it began international passenger flights in May 1935.
The Qantas name comes from "QANTAS", an acronym for its original name, "Queensland and Northern Territory Aerial Services", and it is nicknamed "The Flying Kangaroo"
Qantas is a founding member of the Oneworld airline alliance.
Qantas  ke lifofane ta Australia le lifofane ta lona kgolo ka go fetisisa ke bogolo likepe, vuelos ba machaba le ba celow machaba
Ke lifofane la boraro kgale ka go fetisisa lefateng, ka mor'a KLM le Avianca eka se thehiloe ka November 1920 ba tomile lifofane li e linaheng tsa baeti ka May 1935
Lebitso Qantas tsoa go "QANTAS", e khutsufatso bakeng sa lebitso la ka eona qalong, "Queensland le Northern Territory Aerial Services", 'me e ba mo reneketsa "The Flying Kangaroo"
Qantas ke mothehi setho sa "Oneworld" selekane lifofane.
Finland
Finland ke naga lefasaneng la Europa, toropokgolo ya gona ke Helsinki.

Seo qalong se neng linku te mala sebediwa bakeng sa sekoahelo, empa kajeno go e ka bang feela sebelisa mala maiketsetso
Ke khetheha e ratoang gagolo Afrika Borwa le linaheng ta boahelani.

Yunibesithi ya Fort Hare
Yunibesithi ya Fort Hare  e ne e le tsa yunibesithi bobedi ya Afrika Borwa le setheo se ba pele ba mona go re e fana ka thuto e phahameng go Maafrika
Yunibesithi e ne e le lebaka la sekolo thuto ya bolumeli o ileng ya thehoa qetellong ea lekholo la bo19 la lilemo sebakeng sena ke Scotland be legae la baromuoa James Stewart le mosadi o gae
Seafrikaans buang baagi e ne e tla ga morao go go ngata feela fumana yunibesithi ya gabo bona, e leng ya Yunibesithi ya Stellenbosch.
Yunibesithi e ke ka Tyhume River a Alice ka Kapa Bohlabela le na le histori e ruileng
The sebakeng sa lekholong la bo19 la lilemo ka nako e telele ea etelang makala ntoa lintoeng tse robong khahlanong le Xhosa
E bile feela ka thoko British kolone 
Lipampitana British la naga go ya Xhosa ba neng ba ikemiselitse go fana ka go loanta lehlakoreng la bona 
Fort Hare boeena e ne e lona qalong e British qhobosheane le ba bang lithako ntse ba mo khamphaseng ya yunibesithi tse fumanegang.
Yunibesithi e bile le seabo se segolo seo lihlopha tse ka ntshetsopele ya ANC le mekhatlo e meng ba batsho Afrika Borwa le ne e le khale e tsejoa e le khamphaseng khathatseha
Ka ya apareteiti mehla, go ile ga e le karolo ya Ciskei le ba basoeu ba neng ba sebetsa le yunibesithi, go phethahatsa karolo e phethoang tsoang Fort Beaufort le Hogsback, ile a tlameha go tela moeli go ya mosebetsing ya bona.
A taolo ya le lesha tlas'a Derrick Swartz e tsitsisoa boemo ka 1999 le tsa yunibesithi bile atoloswa go Bhisho le East London
Ka 2015, gape ba kena litaba likgethong bakeng sa lekgotla la seithuti se kgethilego bogolo ba liithuti tsena li bakeng sa DASO
Ka 2016 ka kgetha molao 43% bakeng SASCO  le 40% feela bakeng sa DASO
DASO Leha go le joalo supa ne te ya go re likgethong tsena ka Komisi Independent Dikgetho , empa go ile ga hlophisoa ke op o dia kgwebo ya poraefete.
Seeta
Seêta ke mofuta o mong ya diêta, sekoahelo e sireletang maoto kôtsing ka majoe kapa likhalase bo gale, a batang, lerole le khahlanong toaetso ya letlalo.
Diêta na teo bo golo loma serethe sa me a koahela feela moikong, empa go na le mefuta e mengata le mekgoa e boetse e ikama hantse le fêêne.

Mokete wa Gae Lapeng Concepts o direga letati morago ga Keresemose kadi 26 ta Disemere  le letati morago ga lehu la Morena ka nokeng ya Motsephiri 
Go tlala wa go iia ka diketekete ta batho
Bo rakgwebo potlana ba selegae sa Sekhukhune ka mehutahuta ya bona ba bapata dikgwebo ta bona
Le bao ba nago le bokgoni bja fo DJ ba kena lenaneong go leleta mashaba
Gae Lapeng Concepts ke leano le kgopolo ya Phuti Boshielo yoo a twago Phokwane.

Hillbrow

Orange Farm
Orange Farm  e legôrô 45km borwa wa Johannesburg, ka moka porofense Gauteng, Afrika Borwa.
It is one of the youngest townships in South Africa, with the original inhabitants laid off farm workers, taking up residency in 1988
Support for the population came slowly mostly from people who were tenants at the great township of Soweto.
The Orange Farm Water Crisis Committee, an offshoot of the South African Anti-Privatization Forum  has been very vocal and active against the privatization of water.
Approximately 85% of the people work in Johannesburg
Most of the people use train to get to work
35% of the residents are unemployed and the stats rise every year as the matriculates join them.
Orange Farm is a rapidly growing township with great infrastructural developments each year
The township has a large main clinic  and several minor clinics
The township's main roads are tarred and several minor streets may be tarred but in questionable condition
Orange farm has a small official library, permanent housing for many residents  
Electricity is readily available to most places with only a few areas without electricity 
The town has a large multi-purpose community center.
However, these improvements come with financial costs, which most of the citizens living in Orange Farm cannot afford
The ongoing privatization of Orange Farm has also drawn much criticism from social justice and human rights groups as they have pointed out that local small businesses keep on dying
This can also be linked to the rising number of foreign owned shops in the area
A lot has been done to improve Orange farm, it also now has more than two parks and a two floor mall 
However, nearly all areas still need improvement.
Mountain Road Park  is situated in Orange Farm Ext 2, 1km away from Eyethu Orange Farm Mall.
This park sits where there used to be a soccerfootball pitch of Ext 2 .
Qoqa Secondary School
Orange Farm Secondary School
In 2015, the first stage in the Gauteng Digital Schools project was launched after the second term 
The Gauteng department of education aims to transform all schools in the province to paperless schools
The project is headed by the MEC of education Mr Panyaza Lesufi
The project began with replacing traditional chalkboards with large, touch-operated Smart boards and every learner receiving a Huawei 10" tablet and changes to classrooms
For 2015, the changes were only to grade 12 classes and students
Most  government schools in the province  were equipt with "smart" grade 12 classes
If the project prospers all schools and grades in Orange Farm will be completely paperless and truly digitalised.

Ngwagakgolo 23
Ngwagakgolo wa masomepedi tharo  o tla thoma ka 01 Pherekgong 2201 gomme o tla felela ka 31 Manthole 2300.
Ngwagakgolo 24
Ngwagakgolo wa masomepedi nne  o tla thoma ka 01 Pherekgong 2301 gomme o tla felela ka 31 Manthole 2400.
Ngwagakgolo 25
Ngwagakgolo wa masomepedi hlano  o tla thoma ka 01 Pherekgong 2401 gomme o tla felela ka 31 Manthole 2500.
Ngwagakgolo 26
Ngwagakgolo wa masomepedi tshela  o tla thoma ka 01 Pherekgong 2501 gomme o tla felela ka 31 Manthole 2600.
Ngwagakgolo 27
Ngwagakgolo wa masomepedi upa  o tla thoma ka 01 Pherekgong 2601 gomme o tla felela ka 31 Manthole 2700.
Ngwagakgolo 28
Ngwagakgolo wa masomepedi seswai  o tla thoma ka 01 Pherekgong 2701 gomme o tla felela ka 31 Manthole 2800.
Ngwagakgolo 29
Ngwagakgolo wa masomepedi senyane  o tla thoma ka 01 Pherekgong 2801 gomme o tla felela ka 31 Manthole 2900.
Ngwagakgolo 30
Ngwagakgolo wa masometharo  o tla thoma ka 01 Pherekgong 2901 gomme o tla felela ka 31 Manthole 3000.

1
1  ebile ngwaga wa go thoma ka Moupologo, ngwaga wa bobedi ngwagengsome wa 0s, ngwaga wa pele ngwagengkgolo wa Ngwagakgolo 1, le ngwagengkete wa Ngwagakete 1.
2
2  ebile ngwaga wa go thoma ka Labobedi, ngwaga wa boraro ngwagengsome wa 0s, ngwaga wa bobedi ngwagengkgolo wa Ngwagakgolo 1, le ngwagengkete wa Ngwagakete 1.
3
3  ebile ngwaga wa go thoma ka Laboraro, ngwaga wa bone ngwagengsome wa 0s, ngwaga wa boraro ngwagengkgolo wa Ngwagakgolo 1, le ngwagengkete wa Ngwagakete 1.
4
4  ebile ngwagamolele wa go thoma ka Labone, ngwaga wa bohlano ngwagengsome wa 0s, ngwaga wa bone ngwagengkgolo wa Ngwagakgolo 1, le ngwagengkete wa Ngwagakete 1.
5
5  ebile ngwaga wa go thoma ka Mokibelo, ngwaga wa botshelela ngwagengsome wa 0s, ngwaga wa bohlano ngwagengkgolo wa Ngwagakgolo 1, le ngwagengkete wa Ngwagakete 1.
6
6  ebile ngwaga wa go thoma ka Sontaga, ngwaga wa boupa ngwagengsome wa 0s, ngwaga wa botshelela ngwagengkgolo wa Ngwagakgolo 1, le ngwagengkete wa Ngwagakete 1.
7
7  ebile ngwaga wa go thoma ka Moupologo, ngwaga wa boseswai ngwagengsome wa 0s, ngwaga wa boupa ngwagengkgolo wa Ngwagakgolo 1, le ngwagengkete wa Ngwagakete 1.

Ducati Monster
Die Ducati Monster  is 'n spierfiets ontwerp deur Miguel Angel Galluzzi en vervaardig deur Ducati in Bologna, Italië sedert 1993
Dit is 'n sogenaamde "kaalfiets", wat gekenmerk word deur 'n blootgestelde enjin en raam
Die doelgerigte en deurdagte gebruik van 'n tralieraamwerk in die Ducati Monster is 'n integrale deel van die motorfiets se ontwerp wat vir beide estetiese en strukturele doeltreffendheid sorg.
In 2005 was verkope van die Monster vir meer as die helfte van Ducati se wêreldwye verkope verantwoordelik
Ducatimotorfietse gebruik byna uitsluitlik 90 V-tweelingenjins, wat hul die L-tweeling noem, met desmodromiese kleppe en 'n buisstaaltraliewerkraam, ontwerp deur Fabio Taglioni .
Die Monsterlyn het talle variasies oor die jare heen beleef, van intreevlak 400 cc fietse tot die top-van-die-lyn multiklep, waterverkoelde superbike-enjinweergawes, met soveel as nege verskillende Monsterweergawes in 'n enkele modeljaar
Die Monster se basiese eenvoud het dit ook 'n gunsteling platform vir persoonlike motorfietsbouers gemaak, soos te siene is by tentoonstellingskompetisies soos die Monsteruitdaging
Monsters was uiteindelik verantwoordelik vir twee-derdes of meer van Ducati se produksie-uitset.
BMW S1000RR
The BMW S1000RR is a sport bike initially made by BMW Motorrad to compete in the 2009 Superbike World Championship, that is now in commercial production
It was introduced in Munich in April 2008, and is powered by a 999 cc  inline-4 engine redlined at 14,200 rpm.
BMW made 1,000 S1000RRs in 2009 to satisfy World Superbike homologation requirements, but expanded production for commercial sale of the bike in 2010
It has an anti-lock braking system, standard, with an optional electronic traction control
As of 2016, it has a wet weight of 204 kg , and produces 148.4 kW   13,500 rpm
With 133.6 kW  to the rear wheel, it is the most powerful motorcycle in the class on the dyno.

Maekrosekôpo
Maekrosekôpo ke instrument go bona objects that are too small for the naked eye
The science of investigating small objects using such an instrument is called microscopy
Microscopic means invisible to the eye unless aided by a microscope.
Khamêra
Khamêra is an optical instrument for capturing images, which may be stored, transmitted to another location, or both
The images may be individual still photographs or videos or movies.
Seipônê
Glasses, also known as spectacles, are devices consisting of glass or hard plastic lenses mounted in a frame that holds them in front of a person's eyes, typically using a bridge over the nose and arms which rest over the ears
Glasses are typically used for vision correction, such as with reading glasses.
Thelesekôpo
Thelesekôpo ke instrument, e se fana ya "verkyker", optiese instrument waarmee verafgeleë voorwerpe vergroot waargeneem kan word.
