Botha's Hill
Botha's Hill is a small town outside Hillcrest in KwaZulu Natala, Afrika Borwa
It is the gateway to the Valley of a Thousand Hills
Kearsney College moved to Botha's Hill in 1939.
The village is 37km north-west of Durban, on the old main road to Pietermaritzburg before the N3 highway was built
It was named after a settler, Philip Rudolph Botha, grandfather of General Louis Botha , first Prime Minister of the Union of South Africa.
Cowies Hill
Cowies Hill is a small upmarket residential suburb of Pinetown in Durban, Afrika Borwa
Its eponymous hill is a major feature in the Comrades Marathon which is held between Durban and Pietermaritzburg every year.
Cowies Hill was originally established as farm land and was inhabited by the mayor of Pinetown and his family due to its position overlooking Pinetown
It is situated approximately 15km off the coast line.
Cowies Hill was the site of a farm known as Buffelskop  owned by William Cowie in the latter part of the 19th-century.
Gillitts
Gillitts is a suburb on the western boundary of Durban, KwaZulu Natala, Afrika Borwa.
It is about 35 km inland from the city centre at an elevation of 1800 feet 
Although Durban is semi-tropical and very humid, Gillitts is above the humidity and is not humid, except when it is in the clouds, which generally occurs in summer
It is in the mist belt area, so this area gets a fair amount of mist which many of the residents complain about.
It is positioned near the currently burgeoning Hillcrest and Kloof
The whole area is known as the Upper Highway Area as the M13 highway intersects it.
While some residents do seem to complain about the mist, it does usually come as a welcome relief to the intense humidity of the area.
Gillitts has remained fairly stable while Kloof and Hillcrest in the surrounding areas are growing quite rapidly
This can be attributable to the fact that there is very little area for Gillitts to grow.
Gillitts originated as an extensive farm that extended over the whole of the Upper Highway area, but over time, the farm was sold off and now only the 100-year-old farmhouse remains inside the Gillitts Driving Range and 9-hole, mashie golf course
This golf course is one of the best designed courses of its size in KZN.
The area of Gillitts extends along either side of the M13 highway which stretches from Durban to Pietermaritzburg
The M13 replaced the Old Main Road between the two cities, and a section of Old Main Road is now the major road through the south side of Gillitts.
Off of Stockville Road – one of the other main roads in Gillitts suburb – a large ethnic Indian population lives, and over the traditional Indian festivals, fireworks are very prominent as part of their celebrations, especially over Dipvali and New Years.
On the northern side of the M13, known as Gillitts Park, the old train line from Durban to Pietermaritzburg winds through the residential areas
This train line is no longer in regular use, and is only used by the Umgeni Steam Railway, who runs a tourist service of carriages through from Kloof Train Station to Cato Ridge on the last Sunday of every month
This train is pulled by 'Maureen', a restored Class 3BR No
1486 steam engine built in 1912 and the sound of the train whistle echoing through the neighbourhood on a Sunday morning is a reminder of a quieter time of life.
The Gillitts Train Station on the line in the middle of Gillitts is derelict and currently not used, but is a beautiful example of 1900-era architecture
Dating back to the Boer War in the first decade of the 20th century, the train station was a stop for British soldiers transiting from Durban through to the Midland battlefields as well as returning wounded soldiers.
During the Boer War, the Gillitts family farm held a garrison of British troops, who built a small dam for water and a camp in what is now Camp Road
The dam still exists in a picturesque natural park amongst the houses on what is now Ashley Drive and contains bass, barbel and other fish species as well as supporting a variety of other waterfowl.
The Gillitts Conservancy is a very active organisation who manages the Iphithi Nature Reserve in the middle of northern Gillitts
This nature reserve is a success story
Situated in a valley between two roads, it was a stand of invader species Blue Gum trees for 50 years until 2001
The residents bordering the valley organised a committee and contracted a logger to fell the Blue Gums
As the wood was valuable as timber, the committee was paid a lump sum which it used to found the nature reserve, fence off the additional entrances and pay for the laying of paths, building of viewing decks and planting of indigenous species
Today the Iphithi Nature Reserve is a 15 Hectare stand of indigenous forest, wetland and grasslands and home to many species of birds, small mammals and even a dam has been built which is populated with fish.
The walks and park benches are popular with the residents and the park is quite heavily used on weekends.
With plot sizes of minimum half-an-acre, very few cluster developments, no commercial or industrial development and this very active environmentalist population, Gillitts still houses hundreds of birds and indigenous wildlife including small buck, duiker, Iphithi and porcupine.
In the first six months of 2009, we have seen an upsurge in housebreakings in the area
Traditionally an out-of-the-way neighbourhood, Gillitts Park has been largely spared the crime problems that the rest of the country has experienced
The recent upsurge in incidents has led to the formation of a neighbourhood watch association
Called the Gillitts Park Streetwatch, this organisation is composed of residents who have contracted a service provider to provide cellphone communications links between members
By watching out for each other and working with local law enforcement, the 860-home neighbourhood saw nine arrests of housebreakers in four weeks
The crime rate has since dropped off.
Hillcrest, KwaZulu Natala
Hillcrest ke toropo ya Durban, Afrika Borwa
It is part of the outer West suburbs of Durban.
Hillcrest was formerly a sleepy village, but has now become a booming suburb incorporated into the eThekwini Metropolitan Municipality
"Hillcrest" was founded on a rise in the main road from Durban to Pietermaritzburg in 1895 as a farming or "weekend" village, then a good distance from what was the emerging port of Port Natal.
When the first Hillcrest Health Committee was established in 1943, the total all-race population was 1135 persons and only the Main Road was hardened
Nkutu Road was hardened with klinker in 1947 and this was followed in 1951 with the hardening of the first portion of Inanda Road
In 1962 tarring of selected roads in the central area began, followed by further roads in 1965
By 1971, when Town Board status was obtained, the total population had grown to 2799 persons.
The Hillcrest Waste Water Treatment Plant was finally established in the 1990s, then serving only the central commercial area of the village with phased extensions planned in time, with other areas continuing on septic tanks.
The town celebrated its centenary in 1995 and has since then seen an incredible increase in inhabitants migrating from more central areas in Durban
Hillcrest lost its independent Town Board status in 1996 and was made subject to administration by the Outer West Local Council - a substructure council of the then Durban Unicity
In 2000, the Outer West Local Council, along with other local councils, was disestablished and were replaced by the single eThekwini Municipality encompassing the entire Durban metropolitan area.
The suburb of Hillcrest experienced a building boom in the late 1990s and 2000s with the construction of many gated communities and shopping centres.

Mount Edgecombe
Mount Edgecombe is a gated community situated just north of Durban, KwaZulu Natala, South Africa, part of eThekwini Metropolitan Municipality
It was previously a sugar growing area
The population increased 89% between 2001 and 2011 from 3,874 to 7,323

Cyril Ramaphosa
Matamela Cyril Ramaphosa  ke radipolotiki wa Afrika Borwa
Ke Mopresidente wa bohlano, wa moragorago wa Afrika Borwa, ka lebaka la go itokolla ga Jacob Zuma, ka morago ga go kgetwa ka 15 February, 2018
Pele e be e le moganeti wa kgethologanyo, moetapele wa lekgotla la baomi le rakgwebo, e bile Motlatapresidente wa Afrika Borwa go tloga ka 2014
O ile a kgethwa e le Mopresidente wa African National Congress  Kopanong ya Naga ya ANC Nasrec, borwa bja Johannesburg ka December 2017
, Gape ke modula-setulo wa Komisi ya Sethaba,ref
Lekadipanana
Jacob Zuma

Gwede Mantashe
Jessie Duarte
Chalo Chatu
Chalo Chatu e fetoletsoe e le hore lefatse la rona le ka Zambia ke puo ea Senyesemane ea li-wiki-e fanoeng ka morero oa mahala oa encyclopaedia e entsoeng ke Jason Mulikita ea inehetseng bakeng sa ho ngola litaba tsa Zambia feela le ho leka ho sireletsa histori le boikhohomoso ba Zambia bo buang ka liketsahalo tsa histori le liketsahalo tsa hona joale, batho ba tummeng ba sechaba, lik'hamphani, mekhatlo, liwebsaete, liemahale tsa naha le likarolo tse ling tsa bohlokoa tsa Zambia
Chalo Chatu ke oa Zambia mokhatlo oa Chalo Chatu Foundation, o Lusaka.
Chalo Chatu ke sebaka se sa lefelloeng feela
Wikipedia hore mang kapa mang a ka qala kapa ho fetola leqephe empa o tla u fetola ka Chalo Chatu motho ea lokelang ho ba motho ea ngolisitsoeng le ea tiisitsoeng a nang le marang-rang.
Ho ea ka Chalo Chatu oa COO Chabota Kanguya o ile a re ha a buisana le Mokhatlo oa Zambia oa Hype hore Chalo Chatu ke morero o sebetsang haholo o se nang phaello o khannoang ke sehlopha se inehetseng sa baithaopi ba tsoang hohle ho pholletsa le Zambia 'me kahoo se fumana chelete ka  menehelo eo batho ba e etsang
Bakeng sa ho etsa lipatlisiso le ho bokella boitsebiso litabeng tse fapa-fapaneng tse tsoang libakeng tsohle tsa naha, ba sebelisa litenyehelo tsa lisebelisoa tse kang ho tsamaea le internet bandwidth
Mokhatlo ona o tsamaisang morero ha o na thepa ea oona ebile o itetlehile ka baithaopi ka bomong ho sebelisa thepa ea bona, e kang lik'homphieutha le lik'hamera, ho bokella boitsebiso.

Vietnam Airlines
Vietnam Airlines, stylized as VIETNAMAIRLINES, is the Vietnamese flag carrier headquartered in Hanoi, 
As of 2018 Vietnam Airlines serves 23 destinations in France and operates worldwide scheduled passenger and cargo services to 64 destinations in 17 countries and also carried 22,000,000 passengers in 2017.
Vietnam Airlines, stylized joalokaha VIETNAMAIRLINES, ke Vietnam folakha headquartered a Hanoi, 
Ke ka tlaasana ea
Joalokaha sa 2017 Vietnam Airlines sebeletsa 23 celow Vietnam le sebetsang lefateng ka bophara ho lokiselitsoe baeti le thepa lits'ebeletso ho 64 celow linaheng 17 'me e boetse etsoa bapalami ba nkang 22.000.000 ka 2017.
Julius Sello Malema
Julius Sello Malema  Ke leloko la Parliament le moetapele wa Economic Freedom Fighters, a far-left South African political party, which he founded in July 2013
Ebe ele mopresitente wa African National Congress Youth League go tloga ka 2008 go fihla ka 2012.

Norwegian
Norwegian, stylized as Norwegian Air Shuttle, is the Norwegian flag carrier headquartered in Fornebu, 
It is a subsidiary of the IAG Group and a founding member of the Airlines for Europe alliance
As of 2018 Norwegian operates worldwide scheduled passenger and cargo services to 163 destinations and also carried 33,000,000 passengers in 2018.
Norwegian, stylized joalokaha Norwegian Air Shuttle, ke Fora folakha headquartered a Fornebu, 
Ke ka tlaasana ea IAR Group le setho mothehi oa Airlines for Europe lifofane oa lefate lohle selekane
Ho tloha ka 2018 Norwegian e sebetsa mesebetsi e hlophisitsoeng ea baeti le thepa ho ea libakeng tse 163 'me e boetse e na le bapalami ba 33,000,000 ka 2018.

Atletiki
Lipapali ke likhetho tsa lipapali tse akarelletsang ho matha ka tlhlisano, ho qhomela, ho lahlela le ho tsamaea
Mefuta e tloaelehileng ea litlhlisano tsa liatleletiki ke litekete le timo, tsela e tsamaeang ka tsela, tsela e tolohang ea naha, le morabe o tsamaeang.
Sepedia ditaese
Papali ea chelete ke ho phalla ha chelete kapa ntho e itseng ea bohlokoa  ketsahalong e nang le phello e sa tsitsitseng, e nang le sepheo se ka sehloohong sa ho hapa chelete kapa thepa ea thepa
Kahoo ho becha ho hlokahala hore ho be le likarolo tse tharo tsa ho ba teng: ho nahanisisa , kotsi , le moputso.
Phello ea mopera hangata e potlakile, e kang moqolo o le mong oa li-dice, leqhubu la koloi ea roulette, kapa pere e felitseng qetello, empa liforeimi tse telele li boetse li tloaelehile, ho lumella baeti ho qetellong ea tlhlisano ea lipapali tsa nakong e tlang kapa esita le nako eohle ea lipapali.
Moruba
Moruba li-drafts  ke sehlopha sa lipapali tsa lipapali tsa lipapali bakeng sa libapali tse peli tse kenyelletsang ho tsamaisana ha liaparo tsa seaparo sa uniform le lihlopha tse hlokahalang ka ho qhomela ka likotoana tsa lihlopha
Lisebelisoa tse tsoetseng pele tse tsoang ho tse hlalositsoeng
Lebitso le tsoa lentsoeng ho hula kapa ho falla.
Mancala
Mancala ke e 'ngoe ea lipapali tsa khale ka ho fetisisa tse tsejoang kajeno
Mancala ke lebitso le tloaelehileng bakeng sa lelapa la lipapali tsa lipapali tsa lipapali tse peli tse bapalang lipapali tsa lipapali tse bapalang ka majoe a manyenyane, linaoa, kapa lipeo le mela ea likoti kapa likoting ka har'a lefatse, boto kapa lipapali tse ling
Sepheo ke hangata ho toara likarolo tsohle kapa tse ling tsa likotoana tsa mohanyetsi.
Go 
Tsamaea ke papali ea boqhetseke ea papali ea lipapali bakeng sa bapalami ba babeli, moo sepheo sa bona ke ho potoloha timo e fetang ea mohanyetsi
Papali eo e qapiloe Chaena lilemong tse fetang 2 500 tse fetileng mme ho lumeloa hore ke papali ea khale ka ho fetisisa e bapalang ho fihlela letsatsing lena
Phuputso ea 2016 ke lichaba tse 75 tsa litho tsa Machaba a Kopaneng li fumane hore ho na le batho ba fetang limilione tse 46 lefateng lohle ba tsebang ho bapala Go le ba fetang limilione tse 20 tsa hona joale, bao ba bangata ba bona ba lulang Asia Bochabela

Avro Shackleton
Avro Shackleton e ne e le sefofane se selelele sa leoatle sa Brithani se tamaeang le leoatle se sebelisoang ke British Air Force  le South African Air Force 
E qapiloe ke Avro go tloa libomo ta Avro Lincoln, ka boeona e le tsoelo-pele ea libomo tse tummeng ta Avro Lancaster.
Mofuta ya banana ba ne ba baleha ka 1949 'me o bita Sir Ernest Shackleton, mofuputsi ya South Pole.

Ivory Park
Ivory Park is a densely populated residential area in the east of Johannesburg, in the Gauteng province of South Africa.
Ivory Park is occupied by more than 182 000 black people and is located in Midrand  and falls under the City of Johannesburg Municipality
Services in Ivory Park have improved since the early 1990s
It has five clinics, eight schools, a police station, two libraries and is served by the popular Voice of Tembisa FM community radio station.

Mmuoselegae wa JB Marks

Toropo kgolo-kgolo wa Mmuoselegae wa JB Marks ke Potchefstroom.

Mkhondo NU
Mkhondo NU e akaretsa sebaka ya Mkhondo Mmusogae mô Mmasepala Setereke ta Gert Sibande, Mpumalanga, Afrika Borwa.
Duma nokwe
Duma Nokwe o belegwe ka ngwaga wa 1927,Afrika Borwa.Yena o tseni sekolo Peter's high kua Borwa,gomme a phethagata dithuto ta gagwe Fort Hare university a apara kobo ya thuto ka B.sc degree le Diploma ka ta borutii.O ile a yo oma sekolong sa Kugersdoop high bjalo ka morutii.Kamorago ga o tswariwa kua toropong ya Gemiston o ile a kubiwa moomong ke ba Transvall Department bjalo ka morutii.Go tloga fao o ile a yo ithutela ta bo moemedi.O ile a ahlega ka ngwaga wa 1956.o ile a ba moemedi wa mathomo mo Afrika Borwa yo a ilego a txeiwa kua Transvall Supreme Court.Go tloga fao o ile a swariwa gape ka ngwaga wa 1956,a beiwa trayaleng matati a mararo.Go rile gotwa nhlongswiswi a twela pele le ta polotiki ,a kgethwa go ba mongwaledi wa mokgahlo wa ANC ka ngwaga wa 1958,ka conferentshe ya gagwe ya bo 46 kua Durban.
Tiro Onkgopotse
Abrama Onkgopotse Ramothibi Tiro o hlahile ka la 9 Pulungoana 1947 ho Dinokana, motsana o haufi le Zeerust North West Province, Afrika Boroa
Batsoali ba hae, bao joale e neng e le mantsiboea, e ne e le Nkokwe Peter le Moleseng Anna Tiro.
Tiro o ne a e-na le banab'eso ba babeli le ausi a le mong
'M'ae e ne e le mosebeletsi oa lapeng Emmarentia Johannesburg, Transvaal 
Hanyane ha ho tsejoe ka ntate oa hae
Rangoane oa hae  le Bafedile Masoba  o bile le tusumetso e matla kholisanong ea hae mme o matlafalitse tsebo ea hae ea boetapele
Tiro o ile a qeta nako le malome oa hae moo a mo thusitseng ho tsamaisa khoebo ea ho baka.
O qalile sekolo ka 1951 Sekolong sa Mathomo sa Ikalafeng
Sekolo se ile sa koaloa ka lebaka la litabatabelo tsa basali
Sena se ile sa sitisa lithuto tsa hae
Likhoeling tse 5 tsa pherekano, o ile a sebetsa morafong oa manganese bakeng sa lisente tse 75 ka beke e le mochini o hlatsoang lijana le letsoho ka kakaretso ho bokella chelete ea ho ntetsa pele lithuto tsa hae
O kene Sekolo se Phahameng sa Naledi Soweto, Johannesburg likhoeli tse peli empa a toaroa ka lebaka la tlolo ea molao
Eaba o ea Barolong High School e Mafikeng, Profenseng e ka Leboea Bophirima, moo a ileng a etsa marematlou.
Kamora ho qeta Standard 10 , o ile a ingolisa Turfloop  bakeng sa degree ho Humanities
Mona o khethiloe mopresidente oa Lekhotla la Baemeli ba Baithuti  selemong sa hae sa ho qetela
Moketeng oa kabo ea mangolo a univesithi ka 1972, Tiro o ile a fana ka puo e neng e nyatsa ka matla Molao oa Batho oa 1953
Hamorao e ile ea tsejoa e le "Bopaki ba Turfloop"
Ba boholong univesithing ba ile ba halefisoa ke ho bua ka mokhoa o hlakileng ha Tiro a bua ka mor'a puo eo Tiro a ileng a lelekoa Univesithing
Leha a bile le liponto tsa baithuti ba neng ba le tlasa SRC e ncha, Tiro ha a ka a balloa
E 'ngoe ea likopano tsa hae tsa pele le baokameli joalo ka Mopresidente oa SRC e ne e le ha ba batla ho lelekoa bukeng ea liithuti tse peli tse ba neng ba li nka e le tse "sa lokelang": Mokhatlo oa Barutoana oa Afrika Boroa  Manifesto ea Molao le Phatlalatso ea Litokelo tsa Baithuti
Tsamaiso e ile ea amoha libuka mme ea tlosa lintho.
Ho lelekoa ha Tiro ho Turfloop ho bile le litlamorao tse fihlang tseo batsamaisi ba univesithi ba neng ba sa li lebella
Ka May 1972 ho bile le lintoa tse ngata likampong tsa batho ba bato naheng eohle ho ts'ehetsa Tiro
Mathoasong a Pherekhong tsohle tse kholo tsa batho ba batsho li buelletse ts'ebetso e ts'oanang ea ts'ehetso ea hae
Ka la 2 Phuptjane 1972 baithuti ba Univesithing ea Cape Town  ba bonts'e ba ts'ehetsa Tiro.
Ka 1973, Tiro o ile a kenella mesebetsing ea Black Consciousness Movement 
Leha ho le joalo, ke Turfloop moo ho phatloha ho hoholo ha pele ho bohanyetsi ho ileng ha etsahala ka 1972
Tiro ha a ka a tsamaisa ho phatloha hona feela empa hape e ne e le setsing sa eona
Ka 1973 o ile a nka Tsamaiso ea Setsi sa SASO sa SASO kamora ho thibeloa ha baetapele ba SASO  Black Peoples Convention  ka 1973
Selemong sona seo, o ile a khethoa Mopresidente oa Mokhatlo oa Barutoana oa Afrika Boroa , setho sa setho sa le All-Africa Student 'Union Tiro o ile a patoa Botswana hobane mmuso oa Khethollo ka nako eo o ne o hana ho lumella setopo sa hae ho patoa ha hae Motseng oa Dinokana
Lelapa la Tiro ka ts'ehetso ea Azanian People's Organisation  le kopile Khomishene ea 'Nete le Poelano  ho ba thusa ho khutlisa setopo sa hae naheng bakeng sa lepato hape
Ka la 20 Hlakubele 1998, Mopresidente oa Azapo, Mosibudi Mangena, mme oa Tiro, Mof
Moleseng Tiro le ba lelapa ba amohetse masalla a Tiro moeling oa moeli pakeng tsa Afrika Boroa le Botswana.
Abram Onkgopotse Ramothibi Tiro o ile a qetella a robala Motseng oa Dinokana ka la 22 Hlakubele 1998.
Gordon Mari, eo e neng e le lehloela la 'Muso oa Khethollo, o senotse bukeng ea hae, Inside Boss, hore Tiro o bolailoe ke Z-squad, lefapha la tireletso la Bureau of State Security 
TRC e ile ea hloleha ho lekola lefu la Tiro.
Steve Biko
Bantu Steve Biko obelegwe ka di 18 Mathole ngwageng waebe ele moetapele wa kgatelelo.Motsebalegi wa tsa polelokgatelelo.Moetaplego tsa polelo mokgahlong wa nakong ya lesomesenyane masometshela.maele a gagwe a ile a fitiswa dikuranteng naga ka bophara tsa Afrika-Borwa ka fase ga  O kgodisitswe ke lapa lago topa tsa fase,Biko o goletse lekheiseneng la  kua  ka lesomesenyane masometshela o thomile go ithutela tsa bongaka yunibesiting ya Natal,moo a ilego aba mongwe wa mokgahlo wa  Oile a ba kgahlanong le ba letlalo sweu.Mmogo go bao baso bao ba be ba kgatelletswe ke kgatelelo ya Afrika-Borwa.Oile a kgolwa gore le ge nkabe a ile a ba kgahlanong le batho ba sweu o ile a tlholega ka ge bathosweu ba be ba nale maatla go bathobaso.O ile a tswelela go sebe mmogo le bathosweu ka ge bathobaso ba be bale mokgahlong wa go ikemela legoba ba etapele go tsa go thoma mokgahlo wa  ka lesomesenyane masomeseswai.O ile a thekga maleme a mangwe mo Afrika-Borwa esego fela maleme ao a bolelwago ke bathobaso fela le maleme ao elego .
Cheryl Carolus
Cheryl Carolus  ke o mongwe wa bo radipolotiki nageng ya Afrika Borwa
Yena o belegetwe Silvertown,meagong emegolo ya Cape gola Cape Town
O ile a ba kamanong ya dipolotiki a sa le sekolong se se phagamego ebile a ba molwela tikologo ge a feta go ba o mongwe waba United Democratic Front ka 1983.Ka Mopitlo 1990,Carolus o ile a kgethiwa goba kamanong le African National Congress eo e ilego ya ba poledianong le mmuo wa kgethologanyo gape ka Phupu 1991,o ile a kgethiwa goba o mongwe wa mokgatlo wo mogolo wa nageng wa ANC.O ile a nyala moprofessara Graeme Bloch.Ka 1998,o ile a ba mokomiinara o mogolo nageng ya Afrika Borwa ka London.Magareng ga mengwageng ye ya 2001-2004,o ile aba modula setulo wo mogolo wa matwantle a Afrika Borwa .O ile a ba modula setulo wa di phakhe ta naga ya Afrika Borwa ,ka 2009 o ile a naganiia taba ya go tea setulo go ta difofane ta Afrika Borwa .O ile aba mothua setulo ka khamphaning ya Peotona,khamphani ya dipoloko ebile yago godia dikgwebo.Carolus ke o mongwe wa komiti phetii ya International Crisis Group
Ka 2015,o ile aba moholofedi wa Musiamo ya British .Ka Mopitlo 5,mebele ya batswadi ba monna wa gagwe,Moprofesara Graeme,e hweditwe gola Cape Town ba bolailwe polawo e bohloko.
Fatima Meer
Fatima Meer  ebe e le sengwadi sa Afrika Borwa e bile ele molwantha kgethologanyo .O belegetwe Grey Street,Fatima Meer
ke morwedi wa Moosa Meer le Rachel Farrel ,ke ngwana wa bobedi go bana ba seswai 
Mmagwe be ele thiwana a sena batswadi a dula legae la bana ba dithiwana ,tatagwe o belegetwe Surat ,Gurat
Yo Fatima Meer otere ngwaga yunibesithing ya WIts a be a ba leloko la la Progressive forum ,o ile a thoma go ruta batho babagolo ka bobeyelo bja sefatanaga bja tatagwe ka ngwaga wa 1940 .Mmereko wa gagwe wa dipolotiki o thomile ge anale mengwaga ye lesome upa a le sekolong se se phagamego
Fatima Meer e be ele yo mongwe wa diboledi tse kgolo kopanong yeo e bego e swerwe go lwea mmuo gore o seke wa tsebia molao o moswa wa GROUP AREAS ACT 
Meer le Dr Goonam e be ele basadi ba mathomo go kgethwa goba bagolo ba Natal Indian Congress .O thome Durban and District Women's League ,pele ga dintwa tsa 1949 tseo di bego di thoma ke makgowa go kgaogantha makula le bathobaso bao ba bego ba berekiana mmogo go ta dipolotiki bae bita ANC le Fatima Meer
E be le sekeretari le Bertha Mkhize ,mopresidente wa ANC WOMEN'S LEAGUE bjalo ka modulasetulo .E be ele mokgatlo wa mathomo nageng ya rena yeo makula le bathobaso ba bilego ngata e tee .Mokgatlo wo o tsere mathata sebakeng sa basadi ba maAfrika Borwa bao ba bego ba hloriwa ka lebaka la dipasa ba be ba swariwa ,ya ba ya swara lesolo magareng ga makula go emia go aroganthwa ga ma Afrika Borwa le makula.
Tembeka Ngcukaitobi
Tembeka ngcukaitobi o tswatse ka di 25 tsa mantule 1979 marena tembeka ke moemadi manwadi seboledi tembeka o ngwetse puku ya naga ke yarena ke puku ya mathomo ya go nthiwa kantoraong ye kgolo onale degree ya BPro  LLM unitra LLBrhode LLM london sekolong sa tsa gwebo kalebaka la bjale obereka ke bathaobagage ba moswamawatle ba yemetse makgatlo yo etseng go la zimbabwe
Tembeka ngcukaitobi o bile o mongwe wa ba leloko la EFF yena o tsene sekolo sa unibesething ya transkie ka pasari ka ge a sa kgone go patela sekolo marena temeka o ile a topaseka kantorong babakisana le babang marena tembeka ka ngcukoitobi o go di setwe ke magwe le tatagwe tatagwe a bereka maneng tatagwe o ile a hlokofala mengwegeng ya go feta
Oliver Tambo
Oliver Reginald Kaizana Tambo o belegilwe ka di 27 Oktobere 1917 gola Bizana, Eastern Cape
O tsene sekolo sa Anglican le Methodist sa boruti
O twete pele dithuto ta gagwe go St Peter's gola Gauteng.
Ka ngwaga wa 1943, Tambo, Mandela le Walter Sisulu ba hwedite ANC Youth League
Tambo o ile a ba wa mathomo gpba bosethaba mongwaledi le leloko la bosethaba phethii ka 1948
Youth League e ile ya iinya difetogo ta morero wa kgahlanong le kgethologanyo twetaopele
O ile a ba motlatahlogo ya ANC ka 1958 eupa ka 1959 o ile a hlanka menngwaga e mehlano ka lebaka le go ileta taelo ya mmuo.
O ile a romelwa moe wa mawatle ke ANC go rulanganya kgahlanong le kgatelelo ya kgethologanyo.
boile Afrika-Borwa ka di 13 Desemere 1990 morago ga mengwaga e mosemetharo a le bothopa
Go ile gwaba boima gore a be mopresidente wa ANC ka lebaka la bolweti bja strouku gomme ka 1991 Nelson Mandela a ba mopresidente eupa ka mahlatse ANC ya bopa setulo se se kgethegilego sa bosethaba modulasetulo.
Oliver Tambo o ile a hlokofala ka di 24 Aprele 1993 a nale mengwaga ye 75
Lehu la gagwe le be le le Benoni, Gauteng.
Tambo o ile a kgopela Reggio Emilia moragonyana ga 2005, bo radipolitiki ba ANC ba ile ba tsebia merrero ya leina le lefsa e le Johannesburg International Airport morago ga yena
Kgopelo e ile ya amogelwa ebile ba dira moletlo ka di 27 Oktobere 2006.
Go ile gwaba le palega ya OR Tambo ga Albet Road Recreaction Ground, Muswell Hill ka ntle ga Alexandra Park Sekolo
Ka June 2003 toropo ya Reggio Emilia e ile ya keteka Tambo ka tlholo ya phaka ka boikgafo go Mopresidente wa Afrika Bosetshaba lekgotla
Ntlo ya gagwe 51 Alexandra Park Road Muswell Hill, London e ile ya rekwa ke Afrika Borwa mmusho ka 2010.

1910
1910  ebile ngwaga wa go thoma ka Mokibelo, ngwaga wa pele ngwagengsome wa 1910s, ngwaga wa bolesome ngwagengkgolo wa Ngwagakgolo 20, le ngwaga wa bomakgolo senyane lesome ngwagengkete wa Ngwagakete 2.
1918

Abejar
Abejar ke mmasepala wa profense ya Soria, Castile le Len, Spain
Mmasepala wo o na le badudi bao e ka bago ba 406.
African National Congress
African National Congress  ke mokgatlo wo e lego mmušo wa Afrika Borwa go tloga ka ngwaga wa 1994
ANC e kopane le Congress of South African Trade Unions  le South African Communist Party  go ba tripartite alliance go tloga mathomong a mmušo wa batho ka Mei 1994.
Maloko a thomile mokgatlo wo o bitšwa South African Native National Congress  ka 8 Janaware 1912 Bloemfontein, nepo e le go oketša ditokelo tša bathobaso ba Afrika Borwa
John Dube, e bile mopresidente wa pele wa mokgatlo, ge sereti le mongwadi Sol Plaatje e bile yo mongwe wa maloko a pele
Mokgatlo o fetotšwe leina go ba ANC ka 1923, wa thoma lefego la wona e lego Umkhonto we Sizwe  ka 1961.
Tokomane ya Freedom Charter yeo e ilego ya amogelwa ke Kopanokgothekgothe ya Batho ya 1955, ke yona tokomane ya Motheo ya ANC.
Freedom Charter e bolela gore:
Ka ngwaga wa 1994 ANC e ile ya amogela Lenaneo la Kagoleswa le Tlhabollo , bjalo ka motheo wo o tlago hlahla ANC go diphethogo tša Afrika Borwa
Mananeo a bohlokwa a RDP ke:
ANC e šomišana le South African Communist Party  le Congress of South African Trade Unions 
Lekala le lengwe le le lengwe le ikemetše, gomme le na le molaotheo wa lona le mananeo a lona
Seboka se hlomilwe godimo ga boithaopo go Diphetogo tša Setšhaba tša Temokrasi, le tlhokego ya go kopanya bontšhi bja batho ba Afrika Borwa go ya ka boithaopo bjo.
Makala a ANC a hwetšwa go ditoropo ka moka, ditoropo tše nnyane le mebotwaneng ya Afrika Borwa
ANC e na le ofisi ye kgolo, diofisi tše senyane tša diprofense le diofisi tše mmalwa tša dilete.
http:www.anc.org.zashow.php?id178
African Union
African Union  le legotla la dinaga tša Afrika
African Union e nale maloko a masome hlano tharo .AU e thomilwe ge "African Economic Community " le "Organization of African Unity " di kopana.
Ka 9 Mosegamanye 2002, AU e kwagaditšwe Sukhbir ka semmušo ke Mopresidente wa yona wa pele, Thabo Mbeki .
Dinaga kamoka tša Afrika ntle le Morocco ke maloko a AU.
Afrika
Afrika ke kontinente ya bobedi ka bogolo lefaseng ge go lebelelwa sekgoba le badudi, kontinente ya pele ka bogolo ke Asia.
Bophara bja Afrika bo ka ba 6.0% ya lefase goba 20.4% ya naga ya lefase  Afrika e na le badudi bao e ka bago ba 900,000,000  ba e lego 14% ya badudi ba lefase bophara.
Kontinente ye e dikaneditšwe ke Mediterranean Sea go ya leboa, Suez Canal le Red Sea go ya leboabohlaba, Indian Ocean go ya borwabohlaba, le Atlantic Ocean go ya bodikela.
Afrika e na le dinaga tše masomennetshela  go akaretša Madagascar, goba tše masomehlanotharo  ge go akarêtšwa le dihlakahlaka.
Afrika, bogareng Afrika Bohlabela, e tsebega ka bothomo bja bophelo baithuting ba thutamahlale.
Afrika e na le dilete tše tlhano  e lego
African Union  ke lekgotla la dinaga tša Afrika
Dinaga ka moka tša Afrika ke maloko ka ntle le Morocco.
Afrika Bodikela
Afrika Bodikela ke selete sa Afrika seo se lego bodikela bja naga
Thutafase le dipolotiki tša dinaga di a fapana go ya ka dinaga tšeo di lego seleteng se.
Go ya ka ya Dilete tša UN, dinaga tše tlhano tšeo di welago seleteng sa Afrika Bodikela ke:
Afrika Bohlabela
Afrika Bohlabela ke selete sa Afrika seo se lego bohlabela bja naga
Thutafase le dipolotiki tša dinaga di a fapana go ya ka dinaga tšeo di lego seleteng se.
Go ya ka Dilete tša UN, dinaga tše tlhano tšeo di welago seleteng sa Afrika Bohlabela ke:
Ka thutafase, Egypt le Sudan di wela seleteng se.
Afrika Borwa
Afrika Borwa goba Repabliki ya Afrika Borwa  ke naga lefasaneng la Afrika
"Afrika Borwa" e go la borwa bja Afrika, e wela seleteng sa Borwa bja Afrika.
"Afrika Borwa" e agišane le :
Afrika Borwa ke leloko la Commonwealth of Nations.
Go tloga ka 2004, Jacob Zuma e bile mopresidente wa bolesomepedi wa Afrika Borwa
Pele ga Jacob Zuma, Thabo Mbeki le Morena Nelson Mandela e be e le dipresidente.
Afrika Borwa e na le maleme a lesometee a semmušo e lego Sezulu, Sethosa, Afrikaans, Sepedi, Setswana, Seisimane, Sesotho, Setsonga, Seswati, Sevenda le Sendebele
Afrika Borwa e na le dipolelo tša go swana le Fanakalo, Selobedu, Setebele sa Leboa le SeSan tšeo di bolelwago efela e se dipolelo tša semmušo
Polelo ya go swana le Selobedu le Setlokwa ke dipolelosemmotwana tšeo di welago ka fase ga leleme la Sesotho sa Leboa .
Go tloga ka 1994 ge kgethollo e fela, diprofense tša Afrika Borwa ke tše senyane, e lego:
Go ya ka dipalopalo tša setšhaba tša ngwaga wa 2001, 79.7% ya badudi ba Afrika Borwa ke bakriste.
Afrika Borwa e na le badudi bao e ka bago dimilione tše 47
Go lekanetšwa gore 79.5% ya badudi ke Bathobaso, 9.2% ke Makgowa, mola 8.9 e le Bammala, 2.5% ke maIndia.
Bokamoso bja rena: dira gore bo šome.
Afrika Borwa ke ya batho ba yona ka moka.
Rena batho, re tswalane.
Re phela bjalo ka molalatladi.
Magae a rena, boagišani, metse,
ditoropo, le ditoropokgolo di bolokegile gomme di na le lešata le legolo.
Ka dihlongwa tša rena, re laola maphelo a rena.
Difahlego tša bana ba rena di bolela ka ga bokamoso bjo re bo hlamilego.
Afrika Leboa
Afrika Leboa ke selete sa Afrika seo se lego leboa la naga
Thutafase le dipolotiki tša dinaga di a fapana go ya ka dinaga tšeo di lego seleteng se.
Go ya ka Dilete tša UN, dinaga tše tlhano tšeo di welago seleteng sa Afrika Leboa ke tše di latelago:
Afrikaans
Afrikaans ke polelo yeo setlogo sa yona e lego Sedutch
Afrikaans e bolelwa ke badudi ba Afrika Borwa le Namibia, le ge e na le batho bao ba e bolelago ba mmalwa bao ba dulago Botswana, Angola, Swaziland, Zimbabwe, Lesotho, United Kingdom, Australia le Canada.
Afrikaans ke ye nngwe ya dipolelo tše lesometee tša semmušô tša Afrika Borwa.
Palo ya batho ya 2011 ya Afrika Borwa e bontšha se:
Alconaba
Alconaba ke mmasepala wa porofensing ya Soria, Castile le Len, Spain
Mmasepala wo o nale badudi bao e kabago 165.
Aldealafuente
Aldealafuente ke mmasepala wa porofensing ya Soria, Castile le Len, Spain
Mmasepala wo o nale badudi bao e kabago 120.
Aldealices
Aldealices ke mmasepala wa porofensing ya Soria, Castile le Len, Spain
Mmasepala wo o nale badudi bao e kabago 29.
Algeria
Algeria ke naga lefasaneng la Afrika
"Algeria" e bodikela bja Afrika, e wela seleteng sa Afrika Leboa.
Ka bophara bja naga, Algeria ke naga ya bobedi ka bogolo Afrika.
"Algeria" e agišane le :
Almazn
Almazn ke mmasepala wa porofensing ya Soria, Castile le Len, Spain
Mmasepala wo o nale badudi bao e kabago 5,755.
Amerika
Amerika e bopša ke mafasana a mabedi, e lego Amerika Borwa le Amerika Leboa le dihlakahlaka tša tšona.
Bophara bja Amerika e ka ba 8.3% ya lefase goba 28.4% ya naga ya lefase 
Amerika e na le badudi bao ba ka bago dimilione tše senyane yeo e bago 14% ya badudi ba lefase ka bophara.
Amerika Borwa
Amerika Borwa e borwa ba lefasana la Amerika.
Amerika Borwa ka bophara, ke ya bonne ka bogolo lefase ka bophara, elego 3.5 % ya lefase.
Amerika Leboa
Amerika Leboa e leboa ba lefasana la Amerika.
Angola
Angola ke naga yeo e lego borwabogare bja Afrika.
Angola ke naga yeo e dikaneditšwego ke dinaga tše di latelago
Antarctica
Antarctica ke lefasana leo le lego Borwa bja Lefase kudu go feta mafasana ka moka, kgauswi le South Pole
Antarctica e dikaneditšwe ke Southern Ocean
Ka bophara ke lefasana la bohlano le legolo lefaseng.
Lehlwa le apareditše 98% ya Antarctica yeo e ka bago bonnyane bja dimetara tše 1600 ka bogolo.
Kakaretšo ya boso e bontšha Antarctica e le lefasana le le tonyago, le le omilego gape la diphefo kudu leo le phagamego go feta mafasana ka moka.
Apartheid
Apartheid
Mokgwa wa kgethologanyo wo o šomišitšwe mo Afrika Borwa ka mengwaga ye mentši ka melao.
Mantšu a a latelago a tšwa pukung ya sekolo ya Ditiragalo  ya kereite ya 8 ya 1970
A bontšha gore batho ba baso ba be ba swanetše go phela bjang mo nageng ya bona ka nako ya kgethologanyo
Re šetse re badile gore ke fela palo yeo e nyakegago ya Babaso yeo e dumelelwago kua ditikologong tša ditoropong
Ke ka lebaka leo dikgato tša taolo di tšewago kua ditikologong
tša ditoropong
Tše bohlokwa tša tšeo ke tše di latelago
 Badiredi ba Babaso ga se ba swanela go tšewa go mmasepala wa tikologong ya toropong go išwa tikologong ya ditoropokgolo ka ntle ga tumelelo.
 Kua tikologong ya ditoropokgolo ga go yoo a swanetšego go swara Mothomoso yoo a sa šomego go yena mo mobung wa gagwe goba mo setsheng sa gagwe
Ba swanetše
go dula moo ba abetšwego gona.
 Mosadi wa Mothomoso a ka tsena fela mo tikologong ya toropokgolo fela ge a na le tumelelo ya Komosasa goba ya Maseterata wa setereke seo a dulago go sona, gammogo le bohlatse bja mmasepala wa motse woo a tsenago go wona.
 Monna wa Mothomoso a ka dula tikologong ya toropo fela ge a na le tumelelo  goba ge a belegetšwe moo, goba a šomile moo go
ya ka molao mengwaga ye lesome, goba mošemane yoo tatagwe a šetšego a humane tumelelo ya go dula fao.
 Ditumelelo tša go dula tikologong ya toropo tša Mothomoso yo a tšwago ditšhabeng, di loketše fela nako yeo a lego mošomong wa mong wa gagwe ka yona.
 Badiredi bohle ba swanetše go ngwadišwa lekaleng la mmasepala la bongwadišo
Mothapi le yena o swanetše go tsebiša lekala leo ge modiro wa modiredi wa gagwe o fedišwa.
 Babaso bao ba tšwago mafelong a ka ntle ga Repabliki le Afrika BorwaBodikela ga se ba swanela go dula goba go šoma ditoropong ka ntle ga tumelelo
Tumelelo ye bjalo e fiwa fela ka tlase ga mabaka ao e sego a ka mehla
Batho bao ba thwalwa fela ke meepo.
 Bathobaso bao ba tsenego ditoropong ka ntle ga tumelelo ba ka tlošwa.
Melao ye e thuša kudu gore Bathobaso bao ba šomago ditoropong, e be bona fela bao ba dulago moo
Meloko le bagwera ba bona ba ka no ya go ba etela
Fela ge ketelo ya gona e ka feta diiri tše masomešupapedi, gona moeti o swanetše go hwetša tumelelo
ya komosasa wa setereke sa gabo, gammogo le ya Lekala la Boingwadišo la toropo yeo a yago go etela go yona.
Melao ye e nyakega ka tlase ga mabaka ao a fapanego
Bathobaso bao ba dulago ka ntle ga Repabliki, go fa mohlala, ba gogwa ke dikholofelo tša moputso wo mokaone, mešomo ye mebotse le bophelo bja seemo sa godimo
Ge ba ka tlogelwa go tsena ka go rata, gona ba tlo tšeela Bathobaso ba rena mediro
Bathobaso ba ditoropong le bona ba swanetše go šireletšwa, ka gobane ba phela fela ka seo ba se golago
Phalalelo ya Bathobaso ba ditšhabeng kua toropong e ka dira gore ba amoge ba toropong meputso le dibaka tša mošomo di ka fokotšega
Phalalelo yeo e sa laolwego e ka hlola mathata a tlhokagalo ya dintlo tša bodulo, bolofa, boitshwarompe le bosenyi.
"Thutaleago: Lefase Maabane Le Lehono" Makwela A.O., Van Zyl M.C., Verster T.L.
Arctic Ocean
Arctic Ocean ke lewatle la bohlano ka bogolo mawatleng a lefase.
Asia
Asia ke lefasana le legolo Lefaseng ka bophara ka bogolo bja sekgoba le ka bontši bja badudi
Bophara bja Asia bo ka ba 8.6% ya lefase goba 29.4% ya naga ya lefase 
Asia e na le badudi bao ba ka bago dibilione tše nne  e lego 60% ya badudi ba lefase ka bophara.
Atlantic Ocean
Atlantic Ocean lewatle la bobedi ka bogolo mawatleng a lefase.
August 30
"30 August" ke letšatši labo makgolo pedi masome nne pedi  la Ngwaga wago tlwaelega goba makgolo pedi masome nne tharo tee  ya ngwagamolele.
2001 - Govan Mbeki, moetapele wa African National Congress  - Afrika Borwa.
Australia 
Australia ke lefasana la mafasana a šupa Lefaseng.
Australia ke lefasana la pele ka bonnyane lefaseng ge go lebelelwa sekgoba seo le ikadilego gona, gomme lefasana la bobedi ka bonnyane ke Europa.
Barack Obama
Barack Hussein Obama II o belegwe 4 August 1961
Barack Obama ke mopresedente wa United States of America go tloga ka 20 January 2009.
Barack Obama o belegwe Honolulu, Hawaii
O ngwana wa morêna Barack Hussein Obama  le Ann Dunham .
Batho Batsho
Batho Batsho ba hlaloswa ka gofana dinaga ka dinaga
Kgale ka sesotho, "motho" goba "moafrika" e be era motho yo moso ka mmala, go sa lebelwe gore o bolela polelo yefe, legore o tšwa nageng yefe.
Beke
Beke ke botelele bja matšatši a šupa ao a latelanago
Beke ke paka ya matšatši ao a kgaolago dikgwedi le ngwaga.

Bibele
Bibele ke puku ye kgethwa ya Sekriste.
E na le ditestemente tše pedi: ye Kgale le ye Mpsha.
Ye kgale e dumelelwe ke Bajuda le Bamoslem.
Ye Mpsha e bolela mabapi le go belega le bo phela, le go hlokafala ga Jesu
E tšwelapele go hlaloša go thoma ga Kereke le e na le mangwalo a badumedi ba mathomong.
Bibele ke puku ya kereke
Ke kereke yeo e be e dumelela gore mangwalo afe a be a swanetše go kgobokantšwe go dira Bibele
Kereke e dumela gore ka maatla le tlahlo ya Moya o mokgethwa, e be e kgona go dira mošomo wo.
Binary
Binary e hlaloswa bjalo ka nomoro yeo e hlamago ke diripa tše pedi
Diripa tše ke 0 le 1.
"Bi" go "binary" era gore pedi.
Bodumedi
Bodumedi ke tumelo le ditlwaedi tša sehlopha sa batho
Bodumedi bo akaretša le meetlo ya setho.

Setensele:Afrika
Borwa ba Afrika
Borwa bja Afrika ke selete sa Afrika seo se lego ka Borwa bja naga
Thutafase le dipolotiki tša dinaga di a fapana go ya ka dinaga tšeo di lego seleteng se.
Go ya ka Dilete tša UN, dinaga tše tlhano tšeo di welago seleteng sa Borwa bja Afrika ke:
Ditlhalošo tše dingwe di re dinaga tše di latelago di wela seleteng se:
Go ya ka SADC , Democratic Republic of the Congo  le Tanzania e wela seleteng sa Afrika Bohlabela, di wela seleteng sa Borwa bja Afrika
"Apropos", Southern African Development Community  e hlomilwe ka 1980 go hlohleletša tšhomišano gare ga dinaga  seleteng.
Setensele:Borwa bja Afrika
Setensele:Afrika

Common Monetary Area
Common Monetary Area  e hlomaganya Afrika Borwa, Lesotho le Swaziland go mašeleng a lekgotla
CMA e thekgwa ke Southern African Customs Union .
Namibia e bile leloko morago ga boipušô, e fela ya e kgogela morago ka 1993
Dollar ya Namibia, lilangeni ya Swaziland le loti ya Lesotho di lekana le ranta ya Afrika Borwa
Ranta ea dumelaga ebile ea dinageng tse.
Go maloko a SACU Botswana ke yona fela esego leloko la CMA.
Commonwealth of Nations
Commonwealth of Nations, etsebega gape ka Commonwealth goba ka British Commonwealth, ke mokgatlo wa dinaga tše masome hlano tharo  tšeo di ikgethešego goba maloko.

Dibatsela
Dibatsela goba Nofemere ke kgwedi ya bolesometee ya ngwaga tšhupamabakeng ya Gregorian
Dibatsela goba Nofemere ke ye nngwe ya dikgwedi tše nne tša go ba le matšatši a 30.
Dibatsela 2007
Dibatsela 2007 ke kgwedi ya lesome tee ngwageng
Letšatši la pele ke Labone la mafelelo  ke Labohlano.
Dibatsela 2009
Dibatsela 2009 ke kgwedi ya bolesometee tee ya ngwaga
E thomile ka Sontaga e bile e fela ka morago ga matšatši a 30 ka Mošupologo.
Dibokwane
Dibokwane goba Febereware ke kgwedi ya bobedi ya ngwaga tšhupamabakeng ya Gregorian
Dibokwane ke kgwedi ye kopana ka matšatši ka ge e na le matšatši a ka fase ga a 30.
Dibokwane e na le matšatši a 29 ka ngwagamolele, mola ka ngwaga wa go tlwaelega e na le matšatši a 28
Dibokwane ke kgwedi ye kopana go feta dikgwedi ka moka.
Dibokwane 2007
Dibokwane 2007 ke kgwedi ya bobedi ngwageng
Letšatši la pele ke labone la mafelelo  ke Laboraro.
Dibokwane 2009
Dibokwane 2009 ke kgwedi ya bobedi ya ngwaga
E thomile ka Sontaga e bile e fela ka morago ga matšatši a 28 ka Mokibelo.
Dibokwane 2010
Dibokwane 2010 ke kgwedi ya bobedi ya ngwaga
E thomile ka Mošupologo e bile e fela ka morago ga matšatši a 28 ka Sontaga.

Euro
Euro  ke mašeleng a Lekgoko la Europa.
Europa
Europa ke lefasana le lengwe la mafasana a šupa lefaseng
Europa e bapane le lefasana leo le bitšwago Asia, ebile e ka thokong ya leboa la Afrika.
Leboa la Europa, go na le lewatle leo le bitšwago Arctic Ocean, bodikela bja lewatle le go na le Atlantic Ocean.
Europa ke lefasana la bobedi ka bonnyane lefaseng ge go lebelelwa sekgoba
Lefasana la pele ka bonnyane ke Australia
Ge re lebelela badudi, Europa ke lefasana la boraro, e latela Asia le Afrika
Europa e na le badudi bao ba ka bago 731,000,000 e lego 11% ya batho lefaseng ka bophara.
Federation of Rhodesia and Nyasaland
Central African Federation  e thomilwe ka 1953 ya fela ka 1963.
Fisika
Fisika ke thutamahlale ya dilwana le mesepelo ya tšona.
Fixed exchange rate
Fixed exchange rate, e tsebega gape bjalo ka pegged exchange rate, ke mohuta wago rekišetšana mašeleng wa dinaga mowe tekano  ya go rekišetšana yamašeleng a naga sefetoge ge e bapatšwa le naga yengwe.
Mohlala ke mašeleng a Afrika Borwa le naga tša Swaziland, Lesotho le Namibia.
Fora
Fora  ke naga yeo e lego lefasaneng la Europa
E na le badudi ba 61,875,822.
Free State
Free State ke porofense ya Afrika Borwa
Ka Sesotho e bitšwa Freistata
Toropokgolo ya Free State ke Bloemfontein
Ka 9 June 1995, leina la profense le ile la fetolwa go tšwa go "Orange Free State" ya ba Free State.
Free State e na le metropolitan municipality o tee le mebasepala ya setereke ye mene
Mebasepala ya setereke e na le mebušo ya selegae ye 19 mebušo ya selegae.

Govan Mbeki
Govan Archibald Mvuyelwa Mbeki  ebele molotiki wa Afrika Borwa, ele motswadi wa Thabo Mbeki, mopresidente wa Afrika Borwa
Govan o theilwe morago Edward Govan, "Scottish missionary" o a thomilego Lovedale College, sekolo seo a bego a tsena gosona.
O tsene sekolo Fort Hare University, a phetha dithuto ka 1936  le Psychology mmogo le diploma ya go ruta.
Ebile moeta pele wa African National Congress  le South African Communist Party
Morago ga Rivonia Trial, o ile a golegwa ke mmušo wa kgale wa Afrika Borwa le Nelson Mandela, Walter Sisulu le baetapele ba bangwe ba ANC.
Ka 26 June, 1980 mongwaledi kakaretšo wa African National Congress, Alfred Nzo, o begile gore Govan Mbeki o tla fiwa Isitwalandwe Medal, tlotla ye kgolokgolo ya ANC
Govan Mbeki o be a sa golegile Robben Islandka nako yeo.
Govan Mbeki o tšwele kgolegong morago ga go dula mengwaga ye masome pedi nne  ka 5 November 1987.
Tšhupamabaka ya Gregorian
Tšhupamabaka ya Gregorian e tsejwa bjalo ka tšhupamabaka ya bodikela, goba ya Sekriste, ke tšhupamabaka yeo e šomišwago kudu go feta dišhupamabaka tše dingwe.
Mengwaga go Tšhupamabaka ya Gregorian e thoma morago ga tswalo ya Jesu, yeo e bitswago "anno Domini" .
Tšhupamabaka ya Gregorian e nale dikgwedi tše lesome pedi

Hexadecimal
Hexadecimal e hlaloswa bjalo ka nomoro yeo e hlamago ke diripa tše lesome tee tshela .
"Hexa" go "hexacecimal" era gore 16.
Dirioa tša "hexadecimal" ke 0 gofihla go 9 le "A" goba "a" go fihla go "F" goba "f".

ISO 3166-1 alpha-2
ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 ke dihlaka tše pedi tšeo di emelago dihlaka tša dinaga.
ISO 4217
ISO 4217 ke mephato ya baditshaba yeo e hlalosago dihlaka tše tharo tšeo di emetšego mašeleng a dinaga tša lefase.
Dihlaka tše pedi tša pele ke ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 tša dihlaka tša dinaga ge ya mafelo e le taetšo ya mašeleng
Mohlala ke ZAR-ZA ke Afrika Borwa, ge R ele taetšo ya Ranta
Dihlaka tše tharo di thuša ge dinaga tše dintšhi di šomiša mašeleng a go swana.
Ian Khama
Lieutenant General Seretse Khama Ian Khama goba Ian a Seretse o belegwe 27 Dibokwane 1953 ke presidente ya Botswana gape ke kgoši ya Bamangwato
Ke ngwana wa pele wa Seretse Khama, president ya pele ya Botswana go tloga ka 1966 go fihla 1980, le Ruth Williams Khama.
Indian Ocean
Indian Ocean ke lewatle la boraro ka bogolo mawatleng a lefase.
Integer
Integer ke dinomoro tša makgonthe goba gofelela tša go sebe dipalophatlo go swana le  le 0.
International Standard
International Standard ke mephato yeo e thewilego ke baditšhaba
Mephato ye šomišwa lefase ka bphara
Mephato ye e šomišwa mengwalong, setekniki, goba kgwebong
Mephato ye e thuša kgwebišanong ya mafase le gore ka basetekniti,ba kgone go bolela polelo ye tee.
Iri

"18 June" ke letšatši labo lekgolo masome tshela senyane  la Ngwaga wago tlwaelega goba lekgolo masome šupa  ya ngwagamolele.
Kamela
Kamela ke phoofolo yeo e šomišwago Leganateng.
Kapa Bodikela
Kapa Bodikela ke porofense ya Afrika Borwa
Toropo kgolo ya Kapa Bodikela ke Cape Town.
Kapa Bohlabela
Kapa Bohlabela ke porofense ya Afrika Borwa
Toropokgolo ya Kapa Bohlabela ke Bhisho
Ka ngwaga wa 1994 di nagalegae tše pedi Transkei le Ciskei, le karolo ya bohlabela ya Porofense ya Kapa di ile tša hlomaganywa ya ba Kapa Bohlabela
Bontšhi bja badudi ba Kapa Bohlabela ba bolela Sethosa.
Kapa Leboa
Kapa Leboa ke porofense ya Afrika Borwa
Toropo kgolo ya Kapa Leboa ke Kimberley
Ka bophara ba naga, Kapa Leboa ke porofense ye kgolo kudu go feta diporofense ka moka Afrika Borwa.
Karodi
Karudi ke dinomo tseo di kgonago go arola nomoro go šale lešalêdi.
Mehlala, 10 enale dikarudi tše 1,2,5,10:
Katse
Katse ke seruiwa seo se ruilwego go tloga kgale
Ditau le dinkwe le tšona ke tše dingewe tša leloko le la dikatse
Di lalela dijo tša tšona gomme tša di tabogela ka dinala tša tšona tše bogale.
Ke diphoofolo tše di bolayago diphoofolo tše dingwe gore di hwetše dijo tša tšona
Ka gorealo di tsebega ka gore ke dibata
Le ge katse e ruiwa,e sa na le tlhago ya diphoofolo tše.E swara magotlo,dipeba le dinonyana ka go di lalela
Diphoofolo ka moka tše di jago nama ke tša sehlopha sa dibata.
Ka ntle le go ja nama katse e rata maswi
 Katse e na le mmele wo boleta, wa go menega
Ge o ka šetša ditiro tša katse, o tla lemoga gore e kgona go mena mmele ka boemo bjo bongwe le bjo bongwe
Ge e wa, gantši e tsema fase ka maoto
E koba mokolo ge e befedišitšwe ke mpša
E otlolla mmele wa yona fase ge e lalela nonyana
Ditiro tša yona ka moka ge e tabogela dijo tša yona, ke tša bjako le tša bokgoni
Le ge katse e bonala ka mehla e ke e a tšwafa le go nanya, ke phoofolo ya lebelo le legolo sethakgwaneng se sennyane
 Mmele o khupeditšwe ke boya bjo bokoto gape bjo boleta.
 Letlalo le hlephile kudu mmeleng wa yona
Ge o swara tše ka diatla o kgona go kwa ka moo le hlephilego ka gona.
 Hlogo ke nkgokolo gomme sefahlogo ke se sephaphathi go feta sa mpša.
 Mahlo a magolo a bopegile bjaka a gago gomme a lebeletše pele
Katse e kgona go retolla hlogo le molala go lebelela mathokong a mangwe.
Mmala wa mahlo o atiša go ba botala bja modipa, modipa goba a matala
Ka gare, ga leihlo go na le thaka ye ntsho.
 Ditsebe di na le dintlhana gomme di lebeletše godimo.
 Ditedu tše telele di thuša katse go phopholetša tsela leswiswing.
Katse e na le mosela wo motelele
Ge katse e hlokomela goba e lalela dijo tša yona, e sepetša mosela wa yona bjalo ka diphoofolo ka moka tša leloko le
E tšokotša mosela.
 Katse e kgona go sepela gabosele ka lebaka la mesamelwana ye boleta ka fase ga leoto le lengwe le le lengwe.
 Monwana wo mongwe le wo mongwe o na le lenala le bogale le le obegilego
Dinala di ka gogelwa dipotlaneng tše nnyane, tše di lego menwaneng gore di se kgome fase
Ge katse e nyaka go šomiša dinala tša yona e ka di ntšha
Patiša borofa bjo bongwe bjo boleta gare ga menwana ya gago go tloga ka godimo le ka fase gomme dinala di tla bonala.
Hlokomela gore go na le dinala tše tlhano borofeng bja ka pele le tše nne borofeng bja ka morago.
Mpša ga e kgone go uta dinala tša yona
Di kgoma fase gomme o kgona go kwa motswikinyo wa dinala ge e sepela lebatong
Elelwa gore dinala tša mpša di otlologile mola tša katse di obegile.
Dinala tša katse di kgona go ngapa gabohloko
Di thuša katse go namela mehlare ka lebelo le le makatšago, kudu ge e tšhaba manaba.
Bula molomo wa katse o lebelele meno a yona.
Ge katse e ja nama, e e gatelela fase e e kgerole ka dipolai tše nne le meno a ka morago
Dipolai di šomišwa bjalo ka peke, go gagola nama
Meno a ka morago ke a bogale gape a na le dintlha gomme a a kgohlana ge mehlagare e tswalelwa, bjalo ka magare a sekero
Katse e sekamiša hlogo ge e ja nama gore meno a ka morago a kgone go e sega bjalo ka sekero.
Meno a ka pele mehlagareng ya ka godimo le ka fase, ao a lego gare ga para ye nngwe le ye nngwe ya dipolai, ke a mannyane kudu gomme ga a atiše go šomišwa
Leleme ke le makgwakgwa gomme le swana le maleme a diphoofolo tša leloko leo la dikatse la go ja nama
Leleme le šomišwa bjalo ka raspere  go latswa mašaledi a nama magapong.
Hlokomela gore katse e šomiša leleme la yona ka tsela efe ge e nwa maswi a a lego pirenyeng
E latswa maswi.
Lebelela mahlo a katse
Thaka ye e lego garegare ga leihlo ke lešobana le lennyane la go tsenya seetša leihlong.
Bošego ge seetša se fokola, dithaka di bulega kudu gore seetša ka moka se se lego gona se tsene leihlong
Se kgontšha katse go bona bošego
Ge seetša e le se bogale dithaka di a nyenyefala go thibela gore go se tsene seetša se sentši kudu ka leihlong
Di fetoga mphatšana ge seetša se galefile bjalo ka ge go bontšhwa.
Le ge katse e sa rate meetse, e na le mokgwa wa go itlhwekiša
Katse e swara boya le maoto tša yona gore di dule di hlwekile ka go di latswa ka leleme la yona
E kolobiša borofa bja yona bja ka pele ka leleme gomme ya hlapa hlogo le mahlo.
Katse e ja ka bothakga bjo bogolo
Molomo le maoto, ga di atiše go tšhilafala.
 E namela sehlare ka lebelo ka go šomiša dinala go itshwareletša.
 E otla le go ngapa ka dinala le borofa bja ka pele.
 E kganyelela sehlareng goba kutamong ka lebelo.
 E leka go tšhoša lenaba ka go oba mokolo le go emiša boya le go dira modumo wa go gwaša,
Dikatse di ruiwa malapeng gore e be diruiwaratwa eupša di ka ba le mohola wo mogolo wa go bolaya magotlo, dipeba le dinoga
Batho ba bea dikatse ka dipolokelong, malekelekeng, mabenkeleng, gore di dire mošomo wo.
Lochenr G.P., Dugard H.1971 "Thutamahlale e Bonolo Ya Kakaretšo" Mphato wa 3
Kenya
Kenya ke naga yeo e lego bohlabela bja Afrika
Kenya e bapane le Ethiopia go ya leboa, Somalia go ya leboa bohlaba, Tanzania go ya borwa, Uganda go ya bodikela, le Sudan go ya leboabodikela
E pejana go borwa bohlabela go ya Lewatleng la Intia.
Kgalema Motlanthe
Kgalema Petrus Motlanthe  is a South African politician who served as President of South Africa between 25 September 2008 and 9 May 2009, following the resignation of Thabo Mbeki.
Kgalema Petrus Motlanthe o belegwe Alexandra 19 Mosegamanye 1949
O bile mopresedente wa Afrika Borwa go tloga ka 2008.
Kgati
Kgati ke moraloko wo o ralokwago kudu dinagamagaeng
Moraloko wo o fetogile mo mengwageng
Kgale baraloki ba be ba opela ge ba tshela kgati
Gabjale baswa ga ba opele ge ba tshela kgati, mola kgale e be e ralokwa ka makala a monkgane.
Moraloko wa Kgati o ralokwa kudu ke basetsana, go thoma ka mengwaga ye meraro go fihlela mengwageng ye masomepedi, ge ba bangwe ba kgona go bapala ba le mengawaga ye masomešupanne.
Kgale kgati e be e ralokwa ke basetsana ba bararo
Ba babedi ba swara thapo 
Ba iša thapo godimo le fase gore moraloki wa boraro a tshelele godimo gabedi, a dira bonnete bja gore thapo e se ke ya mo kgoma, morago ga mowe, o tla kwatama fase ga tee a dira bonnete bja gore thapo ge e eya godimo, ga e mo kgome
Ge thapo e ka mo kgoma, thaloko e fedile
Moraloki yo o tla tšwela ntle, moraloki yo mongwe a raloke
Moraloki wa go tšwela ntle o tla swara thapo ka thokong ye nngwe go fa ba bangwe sebaka sa go tshela
Baraloki ba fana sebaka ka go latelana, go tsena moraloki o tee ka o tee goba ka bobedi goba go feta
Baraloki ba tshela ba opela dikoša.
Bjale, melao e fetogile.
moraloko wo o ralokwa ke basetsana dikolong morago ga nako ya dijo ge ba letetše go boela diphapošing.
Kgogo
Kgogo ke nonyana ya go ruiwa gae
Kgogo e na le maoto a mabedi ao a nago le menwana ye mene le manala
Leoto la kgogo le bitšwa monatla  monotlo
Molomo wa yona ke wa ntlhana
E na le maphego ka mahlokoreng a yona
Kgogo e beela mae.
Kgwebo
Kgwebo ke karolo ya papatšo goba tšweletšo yeo e bapatšago ditirelo goba thoto go tloga go motšweletši go iša go bareki.
Kgwedi
Kgwedi ke sekga sa nako goba motšo wa nako.
Tšhupamabaka yaGregorian e nale dikgwedi tše lesome pedi.
Gregorian Tšhupamabaka, go swana le Julian Tšhupamabaka, e nale dikgwedi tše lesometee ngwageng:
Kgwele
Kgwele ya diatla
Kgwele ya diatla ke mohuta wa dipapadi wa go bapalwa ka matsogo
E tsebega bjalo ka papadi ya basadi
Kgwele ya diatla e nyakile go swana le Kgwele ya ntlatlana.
Kgwele ya maoto
Kgwele ya maoto ke mohuta wa dipapadi wa go bapalwa ka maoto.
Mareo ka dipolelo tša setšhaba
Kgwele ya ntlatlana
Kgwele ya ntlatlana ke mohuta wa dipapadi.
Khemistri
Khemistri ke lekala la saense ya fisika leo go lona go ithutwago tlhamo, sebopego, le tsela ya phetogo ge se kopana le tše dingwe.
Kolobe
Kolobe ke phoofolo ya go ruiwa gae.
Kopanobokgoši
Kopanobogoši ke mokgwa wa go buša wa go kopanelwa ke mekgwa ya go fapana ya dipolotiki.
Kurw
Kurw ke motsana wa bohlabela borwa bja Poland, e humanega magareng a Puawy le Lublin
Ke mošate wa gmina.
Magareng a ngwaga wa 1431 le 1442, motsana wa "Kurw" o fetotswe goba motsemogolo goya ka molawo wa Magdeburg
Kage e le toropo yeo e lego praebete, e kgwebišana ka dijo le metsana yeo lego kgaofsi
Difaporiki tsa letlalo le boya tse mmalwa di a humanego toropong ye
Ka ngwagakgolo wa lesome tshela, Kurw e bile kgabagare ga Calvinism, kage bontšhi bja Polish Brethren ba be ba dulo mo
Ka ngwaga wa 1660, badudi ka bonntšhi bo fetogetše go Arianism.
KwaZulu Natala
KwaZulu Natala, ka bokopana "KZN", ke porenfse ya Afrika Borwa
Toropokgolo ya KwaZulu Natala ke Pietermaritzburg
Bontshi bja badudi ba KwaZulu Natala ba bolela Sezulu.
Kwena
Kwena ke segagabi, le phôôfôlô ya Afrika, India le Australia.
Labobedi
Labobedi ke letšatši la beke, le le tlago gare ga Mošupologo le Laboraro.
Labohlano
Labohlano ke letšatši la beke, le le tlago gare ga Labone le Mokibelo.
Labone
Labone ke letšatši la beke, le le tlago gare ga Laboraro le Labohlano.
Laboraro
Laboraro ke letšatši la beke, le le tlago gare ga Labobedi le Labone.
Lebadi
Lebadi ke mokgwa wa go ngwala go laetša dinomo ka tsela erilego
Go hlalose se bokaone, lebadi "11" le hlaloša
Lebadi la roma
Mabadi a Roma ke mabadi a Roma ya kgale ogo šumiša "dialfabete"
Mabadi a Roma lesome, a pele ke
Madi a Roma a šumiša ditlhaka tše šupa go laetša dinomoro, I e laetša motšo, V e laetša hlano, X e laetša lesome, bjalo bjalo.

Leeba
Lefasana
Lefasana le hlaloswa bjalo ka naga ye kgolo ka bophara  yeo e kopanego, e arogantšhwa ke meetse lefaseng.
Lefasana le dihlakehlake di fapana ka bogolo ba naga.
Goya ka dihlaloso tše, lefase le nale mafasana a šupa, elego 
Lefase
Lefase ke polanete ya boraro ka bogolo go tloga letšatšing
Go akanywa gore Lefase ke yona polanete yeo e nalego batho le diphofoolo, ge tše dingwe di se na diphedi.
Mawatle a bipile 71% ya bophara bja lefase, ge mašaledi e le dinaga goba Mafasana.
Legotlo
Lehlwa
Lehlwa le hlolwa ge lefaofao le dira meetse afetoge boga lehlwa gotšwa marung.
Leina la temana
Leina la Temana leina leo le hlalosago temana goba sererwa 
Ge go kgonagala šomiša leina la sepedi.
Lenano la Dinomoro
Lenano la Dinomoro
Nomoro ya prime ke nomoro yeo e nalego dikarodi tše pedi, elego tee le nomoro yeo.
Dinomoro tša Prime tše 100 tša mathomo:
Dinomoro tšago hlamatšega, ke dinomoro tšeo ge o hlakanya dikarudi kamoka tša nomoro  e eba nomoro yeo.
Dinomoro tšago hlamatšega tše lesome:
Lenano la mengwaga
Letlakala le le laetša mengwaga.
Lepogo
Lepogo ke phôôfôlô ya nageng ya lebelo yeo e welago legôrông la dikatse.
Leribiši
Leribiši ke nonyana ya monageng
O e bona bo bošigo fela, e nna le maatlomagolo
E ja magotlo monageng.
Leru
Maru ke dithothi tša meetse tšeo bonalago lefaofaong.
Lesotho
Lesotho, ka semmušo e tsebega ka leina la Bogosi ba Lesotho, ke naga lefasaneng la Afrika
"Lesotho" e borwa bja Afrika, e wela seleteng sa Borwa Bja Afrika.
"Lesotho" ke ye nngwe ya dinaga tše tlhano Afrika, tšeo di sa bapago le lewatle
Lesotho e bapane le go dikanetšwa ke Afrika Borwa
Kgale, e be e tsebega ka la Basutoland
Lesotho ke leloko la Commonwealth of Nations
Polelo ya semmušo ya Lesotho ke Sesotho sa Borwa.
Letlakala la pele
Lethathamo la Wikipedias kaofela 
Letlase la lesome
Letlase la lesome ke lebadi leo letlase la lona elego lesome
Letlase la lesome  di šumišwa kudu go dipalo
"Decimal" goba "Lefase la lesome" difapana le mabadi a mangwe ago šumiša matlase a go fapana.
Notongwalwa ya "decimal" ke go ngwala dinomo go šumišwa "letlase la lesome"
Mehlala ke Mabadi a Roma, Mabadi a Tšhaena, le Mabadi a Arabic.
Letlase la lesometshela
Letlase la lesometshela ke lebadi leo letlase la lona elego lesometshela
Letlase la lesometshela le šumišwa kudu go dikhomphutha le dipalo
"Letlase la lesometshela" le šumiša dithlaka 0 – 9 go laetša nnoto go fiha go senyane le "A","B","C","D","E","F" go laetša lesome go fiha go lesomehlano.
Letlase la pedi
Letlase la Pedi ke lebadi leo letlase la lona elego pedi
"Letlase la Pedi" le šumišwa kudu go "dikhomphuthara".
Ge re šumiša Letlase la Lesome go laetsa letlase la pedi
Letlase la seswai
Letlase la seswai ke lebadi leo letlase la lona elego seswai
Letlase la seswai le šumišwa kudu go dikhomphutha le kgale Amerika
Mabadi a "letlase a seswai" a ka dirwa go tloga go letlase la pedi ka go hloma makoko a dinomoro tse tharo 
Mohlala, "letlase la pedi" la 73 ke 1001001, ge e dirwa makoko eba 1 001 001  gomme lebapi la "letlase la seswai" yaba 111.
Mohlala wa letlase la lesome
Mohlala wa "Letlase la seswa":
Ka go dira dipalo tše, re kgona go bona gore goreng 112 go "Letlase la seswa" e lekana le 6481  73 go letlase la lesome.
Letšatši
Letšatši ke sekga sa nako goba motšo wa nako wo o lekanago le diiri tše 24 .
Letšatši le nale diripa tše pedi tšeo elego mosegare le bošego.
Letšatši le lekana le metsotswana ye 86400.
Go ya ka tšhupamabaka ya Gregorian yeo e šomišwago Afrika matšatši a šupa a dira beke ye tee.

Lewatle, 71% ya bophara ba lefase ke lewatle goba meetse a lewatle
Ka bophara mawatle 361 million km.
mappemonde ocanique Serret

Lewedi goba Setemere ke kgwedi ya bosenyane ya ngwaga tšhupamabakeng ya Gregorian
Lewedi ke ye nngwe ya dikgwedi tše nne tša go ba le matšatši a 30.

Lewedi 2007 ke kgwedi ya senyane ngwageng

Lewedi 2009
Lewedi 2009 ke kgwedi ya bosenyane ya ngwaga

Limpopo
Limpopo ke porofense yeo e lego Leboa gofeta diporofense kamoka Afrika Borwa
Limpopo e leboa la Gauteng
Motse mošate wa Limpopo ke Polokwane .
Go lekanetšwa gore 96.7% ya badudi ke bathobaso, 2.6% ke makgowa, 0.3 ke bammala, 0.3% ke maIndia .
Lingua Franca Nova
Lingua Franca Nova  ke polelo yago hlolwa ke Dr
C
George Boeree wa yunibesithi ya Shippensburg, Pennsylvania
Tlotlontšu ya yona e thewa dipolelo tša SeFora, seItalian, SePotokisi, SeSpanish le SeCatalan
Popopolelo e fokoditšwe
Polelo e šumiša ditlhaka tše masome-pedi pedi.

Dinaga tšeo di bapanego le Malawi ke Zambia Leboabodikela, le Tanzania Leboa, Mozambique bohlaba, borwa le bodikela.
Maleme a Afrika Borwa
Maleme a Afrika Borwa
Afrika Borwa e na le maleme a lesometee a semmušo,e le go Sepedi,Setswana,Sesotho,Xitsonga,Tshivenda,IsiZulu,IsiXhosa,IsiNdebele,IsiSwati,Afrikaans le English
Dipalo tša batho tša 2001 tša Afrika Borwa di bontšha se:
Mali
Mali ke naga lefasaneng la Afrika
"Mali" e bodikela bja Afrika, e wela seleteng sa Afrika Bodikela.
"Mali" ke e tee ya dinaga tše tlhano tša Afrika, tšeo di sa bapago le lewatle.
"Mali" e agišane le :
Manthole
Manthole goba Desemere ke kgwedi ya bolesomepedi ya ngwaga tšhupamabakeng ya Gregorian
Manthole ke ye nngwe ya dikgwedi tše šupa tša go ba le matšatši a 31.
Manthole 11
Manthole 11 ke letšatši labo makgolo a marao masome nee hlano  la Ngwaga wago tlwaelega goba la makgolo a marao masome nee selela  ya ngwagamolele.
Manthole 2007
Manthole 2007 ke kgwedi ya lesome pedi ngwageng
Letšatši la pele ke Mokibelo la mafelelo  ke Mošupologo.

Manthole 2009 ke kgwedi ya bolesometee pedi ya ngwaga

Mauritania
Mauritania ke naga lefasaneng la Afrika

"Mauritania" e agišane le :
Mauritius
Mauritius ke sehlakahlaka seo se lego borwabohlabela bja Afrika, e wela seleteng sa Afrika bohlabela.
Mayotte
Mayotte ke sehlôpha sa dihlakehlake tšeo dilego borwa bohlabela bja Afrika, e wela seleteng sa Afrika Bohlabela.
Mbhazima Shilowa
Mbhazima Samuel  Shilowa  ke tonakgolo ya Gauteng, Afrika Borwa.
Shilowa o belegwe Olifantshoek yeo lehono e elego Limpopo
O phetile dithuto tša gage Akani High School ka 1978
Ngwageng o latelago aya Johannesburg go nyaka mošomo
O thomile go šoma John Weinberg Hardware Germiston
Go tloga mowe aya Anglo Alpha Cement Rooderpoort, morago aya PSG Services - Johannesburg
ka 1981, Shilowa e bile leloko la mokgatlo wa babereki
O kgethilwe goba motlatša moperesidente morago yaba moperesidente wa South African Transport and Allied Workers Union.
Ka 1999 o kgethilwe goba tonakgolo ya Gauteng.

Melilla ke naga lefasaneng la Afrika
"Melilla" e bodikela bja Afrika, e wela seleteng sa Afrikaleboa.
